)@@G@@*********** B#@TOC TAPENAME   AFWILL LIST THE TABLE OF CONTENTS OF UP TOUM
)@@G@@ 999 FILES PER TAPE.    AETOC INTERPRETS THE 1ST FILE'S FORMAT AND GENERUN
)@@G@@ATES CONTROL FIMAGES TO READ IT INTO A TOC-ASSIGNED FILE (TOC$) AND TO LUO
)@@G@@IST    FIT'S TABLE OF CONTENTS, E.G. '@PRT,TL' OR '@ED,RLB'. IT THEN    UP
)@@G@@ EADD'S THESE CONTROL-IMAGES AND IS FINALLY ADDED ITSELF TO   PROCEED WIUQ
)@@G@@TH THE NEXT FILE. AFTHE 1ST FILE FOLLOWED BY 2 HARDWARE EOF MARKS IS CONUR
)@@G@@SIDERED      CTHE LAST FILE UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED.     @]EXAMPLE   US
)@@G@@ ]*******   AFCONTROL-IMAGES GENERATED FOR THE FIRST TAPE FILE (EF ASSUMUT
)@@G@@ED)    ABY USER-SPECIFIED '@TOC TAPE1'  : AC@MSG,N START OF TOC-GENERATEUU
)@@G@@D CONTROL STREAM   ]@SETC,I    ^@HDG    FILE     1     ^@ASG,T TOC$,F///UV
)@@G@@222222 ^@COPIN TAPE1.,TOC$.    #@TEST TNE/0/S2   ]@JUMP JO   #@MOVE TAPEUW
)@@G@@1.,1   ]@JUMP JH   [@JO: ^@PRT,TL     TOC$.      [@JH: #@FREE TOC$.     UX
)@@G@@ [@HDG ^@TOC TAPE1.,,/1/-01   AESIMILAR CONTROL-IMAGES ARE GENERATED FORUY
)@@G@@ SUCCESSIVE FILES.EA1.2.    PROCESSOR CALL FORMAT      A****************UZ
)@@G@@*************     BE@TOC[,OPT]    TAPE[,[USERFILE][,[FILECNT][/STRTFILE#VA
)@@G@@]]]   AETAPE      USER ASSIGNED OR CATALOGUED TAPE TO BE READ.     EUSERVB
)@@G@@FILE  USER ASSIGNED OR CATALOGUED FILE TO BE READ INTO C          INSTEAVC
)@@G@@D OF TOC$. WHEN SPECIFIED,     D          '@ASG,T TOC$,F///222222' AND 'VD
)@@G@@@FREE TOC$.' B          IMAGES ARE NOT GENERATED.      FFILECNT   SPECIFVE
)@@G@@IES NO OF FILES TO BE READ (MAX. 999) INSTEAD OF F          READING UP TVF
)@@G@@O THE LAST FILE (1ST ONE FOLLOWED BY 2 EOF ^          MARKS).      FSTRTVG
)@@G@@FILE# HAS MEANING FOR '@HDG' IMAGES ONLY AND SPECIFIES THE   F          VH
)@@G@@FILE-NO AT WHICH THE TAPE IS POSITIONED. THE DEFAULT   #          IS 1. VI

)@@G@@AGES (FILE TOC$A) BUT LIST     D   THEM. USER MAY ADD BY MEANS OF '@ADD VK
)@@G@@TOC$A.'.    AEB  AFTER LISTING ALL FILES, READ BACKWARDS AND PRINT OUT  VL

)@@G@@KS. FINALLY REPOSITION TAPE TO THE START OF THE FIRST  F   FILE READ BY VO
)@@G@@TOC. B AND M-OPTIONS MAY BE SPECIFIED TOGETHER. ACD  PRINT THIS DOCUMENTVP
)@@G@@ATION, THEN TERMINATE.  AFF  DO NOT GENERATE '@FREE TOC$.' IMAGES. PROVIVQ
)@@G@@DE A MEANS OF      D   ADDING SUCCEEDING EF (@COPIN) FILES IN TOC$.     VR
)@@G@@AEG  @ADD A '@PMD,LP' IMAGE REGARDLESS OF THE A-OPTION.     AFK  MAY BE VS
)@@G@@USED TO SEARCH FOR, AND COPY, ELEMENTS - SELECTED BY   F   NAME/VERSION VT
)@@G@@MASKS, ELEMENT TYPES AND/OR SEQ-NO'S - FROM      ^   TAPE INTO USERFILE.VU

)@@G@@ED CONTROL-IMAGES FOR ALL SELECTED ELEMENTS WITH TOC$  E   AS INPUT AND VW

)@@G@@FILE.' INSTEAD OF '@PRT,TL USERFILE.'      F   FOR ALL PF AND EF FILES RVY
)@@G@@EAD (SEE SECTION 2., ALL DIRECTIVES  F   MAY BE SPECIFIED; SPECIFIED E, VZ
)@@G@@G, N, P, Q AND R-OPTIONS ARE   F   EDITED INTO THE ABOVE IMAGE). TPF$ ISWA
)@@G@@ ASSUMED WHEN USERFILE   E   IS OMITTED. K AND N-OPTIONS MAY BE SPECIFIEWB
)@@G@@D TOGETHER. A]   EXAMPLE ]   ******* ^   @TOC,KN TAPE1.      ^   CHANGE WC
)@@G@@@COPY,A ABS  #   EXCLUDE SYM   ^   MASK NAME/ELTA      F   WILL READ 1STWD

)@@G@@ THIS PROCESS FOR ALL FILES OF TAPE1,      E   I.E. ALL ABS-ELEMENTS ELTWG
)@@G@@A ARE COLLECTED IN FILE TPF$. A]   EXAMPLE ]   *******     @TOC,KN TAPE1WH

)@@G@@ R, A OR O) FOR EACH ONE, WILL REPEAT THIS PROCESS FOR F   TWO MORE FILEWL
)@@G@@S OF TAPE1, I.E. ALL ELEMENTS ELTB ARE COPIED    #   ONTO TAPE2.  AEL  LWM

)@@G@@IST AND/OR MAP ALL SYMBOLIC ELEMENTS A   READ INTO TOC$ OR USERFILE.    WP

)@@G@@ F   INSTEAD OF '@PRT,TL TOC$.' OR '@PRT,TL USERFILE.' FOR ALL EF  F   AWR
)@@G@@ND PF FILES READ (SEE SECTION 2., ALL DIRECTIVES MAY BE      F   SPECIFIWS
)@@G@@ED; SPECIFIED E, G, N, P, Q AND R-OPTIONS ARE EDITED   F   INTO THE ABOVWT

)@@G@@E      ^*****************      #          OR     #          I     AFTHE BY

)@@G@@ ONLY.ACANY NO OF INCLUDE DIRECTIVES MAY BE SPECIFIED.BFINCLUDE   [TYPE-CF

)@@G@@LT 'INCLUDE SYM' IS OVERRULED BY 'INCLUDE TYPE'          SPECIFICATIONS CI
)@@G@@ONLY.  FSEQ    SPECIFIES SEQ-NO'S OF ELEMENTS THAT ARE TO BE INCLUDED,  CJ
)@@G@@ F       SUCH AS SEQ-NO'S A, B THROUGH C, D, E AND F THROUGH EOF.  G    CK
)@@G@@   'SEQ' SPECIFICATIONS HAVE EFFECT ON INCLUDED ELEMENT TYPES      #    CL
)@@G@@   ONLY.     DANY COMBINATION OF THE ABOVE FORMATS IS PERMISSIBLE.B]EXAMCM

)@@G@@E DIRECTIVE OVERRIDES INCLUDE (2.4.1.) AND MASK  ^(2.4.3.) DIRECTIVES.  CT

)@@G@@ THROUGH C, D, E AND F THROUGH EOF.  DANY COMBINATION OF THE ABOVE FORMACY
)@@G@@TS IS PERMISSIBLE.B]EXAMPLE    ]*******   A]E SYM      ]C @XQT ABS CEXCLCZ

)@@G@@EMENTS.     @#2.4.3.    MASK   #**************   #          OR     #    DB
)@@G@@      M     AFTHE MASK DIRECTIVE SPECIFIES ELEMENTS BY NAME AND/OR VERSIDC
)@@G@@ON     EMASKS WHICH ARE TO BE EXCLUSIVELY SELECTED FOR GENERATING  CCONTDD
)@@G@@ROL-IMAGES OR WHICH ARE TO BE IGNORED.     FMASK DIRECTIVES HAVE EFFECT DE
)@@G@@ON INCLUDED ELEMENTS ONLY (2.4.1.). AFANY NO OF MASK DIRECTIVES MAY BE SDF
)@@G@@PECIFIED BUT THE MAX. NO OF     MASKS IS RESTRICTED TO 100. BFM[-]    [-DG
)@@G@@]NAME/MASK1  [-]N/MASKN  [-]VERSION/MASKA  [-]V/MASKX  ]AND/OR     EMASKDH
)@@G@@[-]    [-]N/MASK1/MASK2/MASKN  [-]V/MASKA/MASKB/MASKZ  ]AND/OR     CMASKDI
)@@G@@[-]    [-](N/MASK1 V/MASK2)  [-]N/MASKN   AETHE MASKS MAY CONTAIN FROM 1DJ
)@@G@@ TO 12 CHARACTERS, WHEREBY '*' BDENOTES ANY CHARACTER INCLUDING BLANK.  DK
)@@G@@AEWITH THE EXCEPTION OF 'M ' AND 'M-' DIRECTIVES, WHICH MAY  ENEVER BE SDL
)@@G@@PECIFIED TOGETHER, ANY COMBINATION OF THE ABOVE  ^MASKS MAY BE CHOSEN.  DM
)@@G@@AFWHERE COMBINED NAME-VERSION MASKS ARE TO BE SPECIFIED, THE 2     FMASKDN
)@@G@@S MUST BE ENCLOSED IN PARENTHESIS, I.E. (N/MASK1 V/MASK2)    F(ONLY THOSDO
)@@G@@E ELEMENTS SATISFYING BOTH, A NAME AND A VERSION MASK  AARE TO BE CONSIDDP
)@@G@@ERED A MATCH).    AFWHEN ONLY ' N' AND/OR ' V' MASKS ARE SPECIFIED, ELEMDQ
)@@G@@ENTS THAT    BMATCH AT LEAST ONE MASK ARE SELECTED.   AFWHEN ONLY '-N' ADR
)@@G@@ND/OR '-V' MASKS ARE SPECIFIED, ELEMENTS THAT    BMATCH AT LEAST ONE MASDS
)@@G@@K ARE IGNORED.    AFWHEN BOTH, ** ' N' AND/OR ' V' ** AND ** '-N' AND/ORDT
)@@G@@ '-V' **     EMASKS ARE SPECIFIED, 'M ' OR 'M-' SPECIFY THE PRIORITY.   DU
)@@G@@AF'M ' :  SELECT ONLY ELEMENTS THAT MATCH ' N' AND/OR ' V' MASKS   D    DV
)@@G@@    AND DO NOT MATCH ANY '-N' AND/OR '-V' MASKS.AF'M-' :  IGNORE ALL ELEDW
)@@G@@MENTS THAT MATCH '-N' AND/OR '-V' MASKS    D        AND DO NOT MATCH ANYDX
)@@G@@ ' N' AND/OR ' V' MASKS.AENEVER SPECIFY 'M ' AND 'M-' MASK DIRECTIVES TODY
)@@G@@GETHER.     @]EXAMPLES   ]********  ACMASK  NAME/ELTA/ELTB/ELTC   -VERSIDZ

)@@G@@, TAPELENGTH2,    @I@@@@ . MASSCHANGE, MASSMSKFIL, MASSIGNORE AND MASSSOTC

)@@G@@GMENTED.    @I@@@@ . WHEN CALLING ADDITIONAL SUBROUTINES IN ANY ELEMENTSTE
)@@G@@ MAKE SURE THEY ARE IN THE    @C@@@@ . SAME SEGMENTS OR MOVE THEM INTO STF
)@@G@@EGMENT TOCA.@H@@@@ . ANY MODIFICATIONS TO TOC SHOULD BE REFLECTED IN A LTG
)@@G@@EVEL UPDATE AND THE     @A@@@@ . FOLLOWING RULES MUST BE OBSERVED:@F@@@@TH
)@@G@@ .  1. CATALOGUE THE TOC ELEMENTS IN A PROGRAM FILE NAMED TOC8.   @I@@@@TI
)@@G@@ .  2. APPLY CORRECTIONS TO ANY TOC ELEMENTS, BUT UPDATE THE VERSION NAMTJ
)@@G@@E OF ALL    @D@@@@ .     MODIFIED ELEMENTS TO THE NEW LEVEL (LEVELXX).  TK
)@@G@@@H@@@@ .  3. CHANGE THE VERSIONS OF ELEMENTS TOCDOC, TOCPRE, TOCDEMO, TOTL
)@@G@@CGENRUN,    @H@@@@ .     TOCTESTRUN, (AND TOCDOCWRDNUM IF TOCDOC1 HAS BETM
)@@G@@EN UPDATED TO THE NEW   @F@@@@ .     LEVEL) WITH THE FOLLOWING CONTROL ITN
)@@G@@MAGES TO THE NEW LEVEL: @ @@@@ .        @TOC8.TOC,N TOC8    @ @@@@ .    TO
)@@G@@    CHANGE @CHG,* ALL   @ @@@@ .        VERSION LEVELXX     @F@@@@ .    TP
)@@G@@    MASK NAME/TOCDOC/TOCPRE/TOCDEMO/TOCGENRUN/TOCTESTRUN    @#@@@@ .    TQ
)@@G@@    @EOF    @H@@@@ .  4. CHANGE THE LEVEL REFERENCES IN ELEMENTS TOCPRE,TR
)@@G@@ TOCDEMO, TOCGENRUN,    @H@@@@ .     TOCTESTRUN, (AND TOCDOCWRDNUM IF TOTS
)@@G@@CDOC1 HAS BEEN UPDATED TO THE NEW   @F@@@@ .     LEVEL) WITH THE FOLLOWITT
)@@G@@NG CONTROL IMAGES TO THE NEW LEVEL: @ @@@@ .        @TOC8.TOC,N TOC8    TU

)@@G@@SK NAME/TOCPRE/TOCDEMO/TOCGENRUN/TOCTESTRUN     @#@@@@ .        @EOF    TX
)@@G@@@H@[@@ .  5. MODIFY THE LEVEL DESIGNATION AND DATE IN ELEMENT TOCDOC AT TY
)@@G@@LINE 357    @H@@@[ .  5. MODIFY THE LEVEL DESIGNATION AND DATE IN ELEMENTZ
)@@G@@T TOCDOC AT LINE 83     @B@@@@ .     TO THE NEW LEVEL AND CURRENT DATE. UA

)@@G@@UG 91   07:34:23     172             50    5   0   1 0000020     17532  EU
)@@G@@@O@[@@   PKTGEN$       G*[S@@@*SDFF*@]@F@DQDAABC,20   @]@G@FQDAABC,1    EV
)@@G@@@]@@@GQDAABC,20   @]@F@D*H3M9/MS    @]@@@D*H3M9/MS    @]@@@H*H3M9/MS    EW
)@@G@@@ @E@D+RUN  XDTST,SCM097/H3M9,MON,20@ @@@E+RUN  XDTST,SCB097/H3M9,MON,20EX
)@@G@@@#@@@D+PRT,F  TPF$.     @#@@@D+ED,I   TPF$.ELT1 @E@@@D      SUBROUTINE LEY
)@@G@@NPLOT (VECT,HEADR,PRNAME,DATE,SWITCH)     @F@@@D      DIMENSION LINE(97)EZ
)@@G@@,TIME(25),VECT(97),HEADR(7),BORDER(3)     @^@@@D      DIMENSION DATE(2) FA
)@@G@@@^@@@D      LOGICAL SWITCH    @D@@@D      INTEGER TITLE(3)/' TOTAL',' REFB
)@@G@@SPO','NSE   '/    @B@@@D      INTEGER TIME,BORDER,DATE,PRNAME     @#@@@DFC
)@@G@@      SCALE=2.0*10@^@@@D      WRITE (6,13) HEADR@^@@@D      DO 9 I=50,1,FD
)@@G@@-1    @#@@@D      J=I/10*10   @#@@@D      DO 3 N=1,3  @^@@@D    3 BORDERFE
)@@G@@(N)='      '@ @@@D      IF (I.NE.33) GO TO 5    @^@@@D      BORDER(1)=TIFF
)@@G@@TLE(1)@A@@@D      IF(SWITCH) BORDER(1)=PRNAME   @#@@@D      DO 4 L=2,3  FG
)@@G@@@^@@@D    4 BORDER(L)=TITLE(L)@#@@@D    5 CONTINUE    @#@@@D      DO 6 KFH
)@@G@@=2,97 @^@@@D    6 LINE(K)='      '  @#@@@D      LINE(1)='I' @ @@@D      FI
)@@G@@IF (I.NE.J) GO TO 7     @#@@@D      LINE(1)='-' @^@@@D      VALUE-SCALE*FJ
)@@G@@J/50  @#@@@D    7 CONTINUE    @#@@@D      DO 8 L=1,96 @C@@@D      IF (VEFK
)@@G@@CT(L)*50/SCALE.GT.I-1) LINE(L+1)='*'@#@@@D    8 CONTINUE    @B@@@D      FL
)@@G@@IF (I.EQ.J) WRITE (6,14) VALUE,LINE @B@@@D      IF (I.NE.J) WRITE (6,15)FM
)@@G@@ BORDER,LINE@#@@@D    9 CONTINUE    @#@@@D      DO 10 I=1,97@#@@@D   10 FN
)@@G@@LINE(I)='-' @^@@@D      DO 11 I=1,97,4    @#@@@D   11 LINE(I)='I' @#@@@DFO
)@@G@@      BORDER(3)=0 @A@@@D      WRITE (6,14) BORDER(3),LINE   @#@@@D      FP
)@@G@@DO 12 I=1,25@^@@@D   12 TIMEEI)=(I-1)     @^@@@D      WRITE (6,16) TIME FQ
)@@G@@@A@@@D      WRITE(6,17) DATE(1),DATE(2)   @]@@@D      RETURN@[@@@DC     FR
)@@G@@@ @@@D13    FORMAT(1H1,51X,7A6//)   @ @@@D   14 FORMAT (1X,1PG18.7,97A1)FS
)@@G@@@ @@@D   15 FORMAT (1X,3A6,97A1)    @^@@@D   16 FORMAT (16X,25I4) @C@@@DFT
)@@G@@   17 FORMAT (61X,'TIME (HOURS)',//61X,2A6)     @]@@@D      END   @^@@@DFU
)@@G@@+FOR,E   TPF$.ELT1,TPF$.@[@@@D+PRT,T@#@@@D+ED,U    TPF$.ELT1@[@@@D39    FV
)@@G@@@#@@@DC /TIMEE/TIME(/   @[@@@D24    @]@@@DC /-/=/     @[@@@DP     @[@@@DFW
)@@G@@-4    @[@@@DO 4   @[@@@DEXI   @ @@@D+FOR,E  TPF$.ELT1,TPF$.ELT2   @#@@@DFX
)@@G@@+MAP,I  A,ABS     @#@@@DIN   TPF$.MAIN    @#@@@DIN   TPF$.ELT2    @[@@@DFY
)@@G@@END   @]@@@D+ED,U  A    @#@@@DC /MAIN/MAIN1/    @[@@@DEXI   @#@@@D+COPY,FZ
)@@G@@S   A,B     @]@@@D+ED,I RAND  @^@@@D          AXR$      .   @]@@@D$(6)  GA
)@@G@@    . @B@@@DPF        FORM      12,6,18             . @^@@@DPRBUF     +0GB
)@@G@@        .   @^@@@D          +0        .   @]@@@D$(1)      . @[@@@DSTART GC
)@@G@@@F@@@D          SR        R2,SEED             . SET RANDOM NUM SEED     GD
)@@G@@@B@@@D          LMJ       X!1,NRAND            .@#@@@DDATA      +SEED   GE
)@@G@@@]@@@D          +0@B@@@D          L         A0,*DATA             .@B@@@DGF
)@@G@@          LMJ       X11,L$BOCT          . @B@@@D          DS        A1,PGG
)@@G@@RBUF            . @B@@@D          L         A0,(PF 1,2,PRBUF)   . @B@@@DGH
)@@G@@          ER        PRINT$              . @B@@@D          L,U       A1,5GI
)@@G@@000             . @B@@@D          ER        TWAIT$              . @B@@@DGJ
)@@G@@          J         START+1             . @B@@@D          ER        EXITGK
)@@G@@$               . @ @@@D          END       START     @[@@@D+PRT,T@[@@@DGL
)@@G@@+PACK @#@@@D+MASM,E   RAND    @]@@@D+ED,U   RAND@[@@@D9     @]@@@DC /X!1GM
)@@G@@/X11/ @[@@@DP     @[@@@D-4    @[@@@DO 7   @]@@@D+ELT,L  RAND@[@@@D+END  GN
)@@G@@@]@@@D+ERS   TPF$.@#@@@D+PRT,F  TPF$.     @#@@@D+ED,I   TPF$.ELT1 @E@@@DGO
)@@G@@      SUBROUTINE LNPLOT (VECT,HEADR,PRNAME,DATE,SWITCH)     @F@@@D      GP
)@@G@@DIMENSION LINE(97),TIME(25),VECT(97),HEADR(7),BORDER(3)     @^@@@D      GQ
)@@G@@DIMENSION DATE(2) @^@@@D      LOGICAL SWITCH    @D@@@D      INTEGER TITLGR
)@@G@@E(3)/' TOTAL',' RESPO','NSE   '/    @B@@@D      INTEGER TIME,BORDER,DATEGS
)@@G@@,PRNAME     @#@@@D      SCALE=2.0*10@^@@@D      WRITE (6,13) HEADR@^@@@DGT
)@@G@@      DO 9 I=50,1,-1    @#@@@D      J=I/10*10   @#@@@D      DO 3 N=1,3  GU
)@@G@@@^@@@D    3 BORDER(N)='      '@ @@@D      IF (I.NE.33) GO TO 5    @^@@@DGV
)@@G@@      BORDER(1)=TITLE(1)@A@@@D      IF(SWITCH) BORDER(1)=PRNAME   @#@@@DGW
)@@G@@      DO 4 L=2,3  @^@@@D    4 BORDER(L)=TITLE(L)@#@@@D    5 CONTINUE    GX
)@@G@@@#@@@D      DO 6 K=2,97 @^@@@D    6 LINE(K)='      '  @#@@@D      LINE(1GY
)@@G@@)='I' @ @@@D      IF (I.NE.J) GO TO 7     @#@@@D      LINE(1)='-' @^@@@DGZ
)@@G@@      VALUE-SCALE*J/50  @#@@@D    7 CONTINUE    @#@@@D      DO 8 L=1,96 HA
)@@G@@@C@@@D      IF (VECT(L)*50/SCALE.GT.I-1) LINE(L+1)='*'@#@@@D    8 CONTINHB
)@@G@@UE    @B@@@D      IF (I.EQ.J) WRITE (6,14) VALUE,LINE @B@@@D      IF (I.HC
)@@G@@NE.J) WRITE (6,15) BORDER,LINE@#@@@D    9 CONTINUE    @#@@@D      DO 10 HD
)@@G@@I=1,97@#@@@D   10 LINE(I)='-' @^@@@D      DO 11 I=1,97,4    @#@@@D   11 HE
)@@G@@LINE(I)='I' @#@@@D      BORDER(3)=0 @A@@@D      WRITE (6,14) BORDER(3),LHF
)@@G@@INE   @#@@@D      DO 12 I=1,25@^@@@D   12 TIMEEI)=(I-1)     @^@@@D      HG
)@@G@@WRITE (6,16) TIME @A@@@D      WRITE(6,17) DATE(1),DATE(2)   @]@@@D      HH
)@@G@@RETURN@[@@@DC     @ @@@D13    FORMAT(1H1,51X,7A6//)   @ @@@D   14 FORMATHI
)@@G@@ (1X,1PG18.7,97A1)@ @@@D   15 FORMAT (1X,3A6,97A1)    @^@@@D   16 FORMATHJ
)@@G@@ (16X,25I4) @C@@@D   17 FORMAT (61X,'TIME (HOURS)',//61X,2A6)     @]@@@DHK
)@@G@@      END   @^@@@D+FOR,E   TPF$.ELT1,TPF$.@[@@@D+PRT,T@#@@@D+ED,U    TPFHL
)@@G@@$.ELT1@[@@@D39    @#@@@DC /TIMEE/TIME(/   @[@@@D24    @]@@@DC /-/=/     HM
)@@G@@@[@@@DP     @[@@@D-4    @[@@@DO 4   @[@@@DEXI   @ @@@D+FOR,E  TPF$.ELT1,HN
)@@G@@TPF$.ELT2   @#@@@D+MAP,I  A,ABS     @#@@@DIN   TPF$.MAIN    @#@@@DIN   THO
)@@G@@PF$.ELT2    @[@@@DEND   @]@@@D+ED,U  A    @#@@@DC /MAIN/MAIN1/    @[@@@DHP
)@@G@@EXI   @#@@@D+COPY,S   A,B     @]@@@D+ED,I RAND  @^@@@D          AXR$    HQ
)@@G@@  .   @]@@@D$(6)      . @B@@@DPF        FORM      12,6,18             . HR
)@@G@@@^@@@DPRBUF     +0        .   @^@@@D          +0        .   @]@@@D$(1)  HS
)@@G@@    . @[@@@DSTART @F@@@D          SR        R2,SEED             . SET RAHT
)@@G@@NDOM NUM SEED     @B@@@D          LMJ       X!1,NRAND            .@#@@@DHU
)@@G@@DATA      +SEED   @]@@@D          +0@B@@@D          L         A0,*DATA  HV
)@@G@@           .@B@@@D          LMJ       X11,L$BOCT          . @B@@@D      HW
)@@G@@    DS        A1,PRBUF            . @B@@@D          L         A0,(PF 1,2HX
)@@G@@,PRBUF)   . @B@@@D          ER        PRINT$              . @B@@@D      HY
)@@G@@    L,U       A1,5000             . @B@@@D          ER        TWAIT$    HZ
)@@G@@          . @B@@@D          J         START+1             . @B@@@D      IA
)@@G@@    ER        EXIT$               . @ @@@D          END       START     IB
)@@G@@@[@@@D+PRT,T@[@@@D+PACK @#@@@D+MASM,E   RAND    @]@@@D+ED,U   RAND@[@@@DIC
)@@G@@9     @]@@@DC /X!1/X11/ @[@@@DP     @[@@@D-4    @[@@@DO 7   @]@@@D+ELT,LID
)@@G@@  RAND@[@@@D+END  @]@@@D+ERS   TPF$.@#@@@D+PRT,F  TPF$.     @#@@@D+ED,I IE
)@@G@@  TPF$.ELT1 @E@@@D      SUBROUTINE LNPLOT (VECT,HEADR,PRNAME,DATE,SWITCHIF
)@@G@@)     @F@@@D      DIMENSION LINE(97),TIME(25),VECT(97),HEADR(7),BORDER(3IG
)@@G@@)     @^@@@D      DIMENSION DATE(2) @^@@@D      LOGICAL SWITCH    @D@@@DIH
)@@G@@      INTEGER TITLE(3)/' TOTAL',' RESPO','NSE   '/    @B@@@D      INTEGEII
)@@G@@R TIME,BORDER,DATE,PRNAME     @#@@@D      SCALE=2.0*10@^@@@D      WRITE IJ
)@@G@@(6,13) HEADR@^@@@D      DO 9 I=50,1,-1    @#@@@D      J=I/10*10   @#@@@DIK
)@@G@@      DO 3 N=1,3  @^@@@D    3 BORDER(N)='      '@ @@@D      IF (I.NE.33)IL
)@@G@@ GO TO 5    @^@@@D      BORDER(1)=TITLE(1)@A@@@D      IF(SWITCH) BORDER(IM
)@@G@@1)=PRNAME   @#@@@D      DO 4 L=2,3  @^@@@D    4 BORDER(L)=TITLE(L)@#@@@DIN
)@@G@@    5 CONTINUE    @#@@@D      DO 6 K=2,97 @^@@@D    6 LINE(K)='      '  IO
)@@G@@@#@@@D      LINE(1)='I' @ @@@D      IF (I.NE.J) GO TO 7     @#@@@D      IP
)@@G@@LINE(1)='-' @^@@@D      VALUE-SCALE*J/50  @#@@@D    7 CONTINUE    @#@@@DIQ
)@@G@@      DO 8 L=1,96 @C@@@D      IF (VECT(L)*50/SCALE.GT.I-1) LINE(L+1)='*'IR
)@@G@@@#@@@D    8 CONTINUE    @B@@@D      IF (I.EQ.J) WRITE (6,14) VALUE,LINE IS
)@@G@@@B@@@D      IF (I.NE.J) WRITE (6,15) BORDER,LINE@#@@@D    9 CONTINUE    IT
)@@G@@@#@@@D      DO 10 I=1,97@#@@@D   10 LINE(I)='-' @^@@@D      DO 11 I=1,97IU
)@@G@@,4    @#@@@D   11 LINE(I)='I' @#@@@D      BORDER(3)=0 @A@@@D      WRITE IV
)@@G@@(6,14) BORDER(3),LINE   @#@@@D      DO 12 I=1,25@^@@@D   12 TIMEEI)=(I-1IW
)@@G@@)     @^@@@D      WRITE (6,16) TIME @A@@@D      WRITE(6,17) DATE(1),DATEIX
)@@G@@(2)   @]@@@D      RETURN@[@@@DC     @ @@@D13    FORMAT(1H1,51X,7A6//)   IY
)@@G@@@ @@@D   14 FORMAT (1X,1PG18.7,97A1)@ @@@D   15 FORMAT (1X,3A6,97A1)    IZ
)@@G@@@^@@@D   16 FORMAT (16X,25I4) @C@@@D   17 FORMAT (61X,'TIME (HOURS)',//6JA
)@@G@@1X,2A6)     @]@@@D      END   @^@@@D+FOR,E   TPF$.ELT1,TPF$.@[@@@D+PRT,TJB
)@@G@@@#@@@D+ED,U    TPF$.ELT1@[@@@D39    @#@@@DC /TIMEE/TIME(/   @[@@@D24    JC
)@@G@@@]@@@DC /-/=/     @[@@@DP     @[@@@D-4    @[@@@DO 4   @[@@@DEXI   @ @@@DJD
)@@G@@+FOR,E  TPF$.ELT1,TPF$.ELT2   @#@@@D+MAP,I  A,ABS     @#@@@DIN   TPF$.MAJE
)@@G@@IN    @#@@@DIN   TPF$.ELT2    @[@@@DEND   @]@@@D+ED,U  A    @#@@@DC /MAIJF
)@@G@@N/MAIN1/    @[@@@DEXI   @#@@@D+COPY,S   A,B     @]@@@D+ED,I RAND  @^@@@DJG
)@@G@@          AXR$      .   @]@@@D$(6)      . @B@@@DPF        FORM      12,6JH
)@@G@@,18             . @^@@@DPRBUF     +0        .   @^@@@D          +0      JI
)@@G@@  .   @]@@@D$(1)      . @[@@@DSTART @F@@@D          SR        R2,SEED   JJ
)@@G@@          . SET RANDOM NUM SEED     @B@@@D          LMJ       X!1,NRAND JK
)@@G@@           .@#@@@DDATA      +SEED   @]@@@D          +0@B@@@D          L JL
)@@G@@        A0,*DATA             .@B@@@D          LMJ       X11,L$BOCT      JM
)@@G@@    . @B@@@D          DS        A1,PRBUF            . @B@@@D          L JN
)@@G@@        A0,(PF 1,2,PRBUF)   . @B@@@D          ER        PRINT$          JO
)@@G@@    . @B@@@D          L,U       A1,5000             . @B@@@D          ERJP
)@@G@@        TWAIT$              . @B@@@D          J         START+1         JQ
)@@G@@    . @B@@@D          ER        EXIT$               . @ @@@D          ENJR
)@@G@@D       START     @[@@@D+PRT,T@[@@@D+PACK @#@@@D+MASM,E   RAND    @]@@@DJS
)@@G@@+ED,U   RAND@[@@@D9     @]@@@DC /X!1/X11/ @[@@@DP     @[@@@D-4    @[@@@DJT
)@@G@@O 7   @]@@@D+ELT,L  RAND@[@@@D+END  @]@@@D+ERS   TPF$.@[@@@D+FIN  @[@@@DJU
)@@G@@@EOF  _@@@@@^@)D-DD1  @1 C.^8!^8)^@)@A@@@C^@)^@)^@)E1[D-PC*!ET#CDGC*%DK\JV
)@@G@@)@M[Y@S@@@@@@@[@@Q@@[@@N@@[@@N@@[@@N@@[@@N@@[@@N@@[@@N@@[@@N@@[@@N@@[@@NJW
)@@G@@@@[@@NAA@@@@)@X[Y@S@@@@@@@I@]]@@H@[3@@G@[&@@F@[R@@E@[D@@D@@'@@C@@?@@B@@>JX
)@@G@@@@A@@Z@@ @@V@@^@@QAB@@@@)@*@I@S@@@@@)@E@Q@S@@@@@)@I@&@S]&@C@]@@@@^@@@@@JJY
)@@G@@@@A@@L@@@@]]C*)@@@C1ODDH@@J@]#AC@@@@)@(@I@S@@@@@)@@[]@]&@@@@9(%@@BA]'@@AJZ
)@@G@@R')@@@C@)@@E/KF@@@R]%@@D9!%@@BR]'@@A______AD@@@@)@C[]@@@@@@@)@I@K@C1ODDHKA

)@@G@@).EQ.0) OMITS(I,2)=1000 @#@@@Q1113  CONTINUE    @F@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRCQ
)@@G@@ITE(6,1031)((OMITS(I,I2),I2=1,2),I=1,NUOMI)     @#@@@Q5     CONTINUE    CR
)@@G@@@A@@@Q      IF(PARAM.NE.'START ') GO TO 6 @ @@@Q      READ(5,103) SDATE,CS
)@@G@@X4    @ @@@Q      WRITE(6,203) SDATE,X4   @^@@@Q      X5=X4/100*100     CT
)@@G@@@#@@@Q      X4=X4-X5    @^@@@Q      TEMPS=X5*36+X4*60 @ @@@Q      IF(TEMCU
)@@G@@PS.EQ.0) TEMPS=1  @#@@@Q      STIME=TEMPS @A@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,CV
)@@G@@100) SDATE  @A@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,300) STIME  @#@@@Q6     CONTINCW
)@@G@@UE    @A@@@Q      IF(PARAM.NE.'FINISH') GO TO 7 @ @@@Q      READ(5,103) CX
)@@G@@VDATE,X4    @ @@@Q      WRITE(6,203) VDATE,X4   @^@@@Q      X5=X4/100*10CY
)@@G@@0     @#@@@Q      X4=X4-X5    @^@@@Q      TEMPS=X5*36+X4*60 @ @@@Q      CZ
)@@G@@IF(TEMPS.EQ.0) TEMPS=1  @#@@@Q      FTIME=TEMPS @A@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRDA
)@@G@@ITE(6,100) VDATE  @A@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,300) FTIME  @#@@@Q7     DB
)@@G@@CONTINUE    @A@@@Q      IF(PARAM.NE.'TODAY ') GO TO 8 @^@@@Q      CALL ADC
)@@G@@DATE(D,T)   @A@@@Q      BITS(SDATE,1,36)=BITS(D,1,36) @B@@@Q      BITS(SDD
)@@G@@DATE,37,18)=BITS(D,37,18)     @A@@@Q      BITS(VDATE,1,36)=BITS(D,1,36) DE
)@@G@@@B@@@Q      BITS(VDATE,37,18)=BITS(D,37,18)     @#@@@Q      STIME=0     DF
)@@G@@@#@@@Q      FTIME=86400 @B@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,100) SDATE,VDATE  DG
)@@G@@@B@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,300) STIME,FTIME  @#@@@Q8     CONTINUE    DH
)@@G@@@A@@@Q      IF(PARAM.NE.'YESTER') GO TO 12@^@@@Q      CALL ADATE(D,T)   DI
)@@G@@@E@@@Q      BITS(START,1,6)=(10*(BITS(D,1,6)-48))+(BITS(D,7,6)-48)@C@@@QDJ
)@@G@@      BITS(START,7,6)=(10*(BITS(D,13,6)-48))+   @ @@@Q     *(BITS(D,19,6DK
)@@G@@)-48)-1     @C@@@Q      BITS(START,13,6)=(10*(BITS(D,25,6)-48))+  @ @@@QDL
)@@G@@     * (BITS(D,31,6)-48)-77   @B@@@Q      IF(BITS(START,7,6).NE.0) GO TODM
)@@G@@ 10   @B@@@Q      BITS(START,1,6)=BITS(START,1,6)-1   @^@@@Q      A=BITSDN
)@@G@@(START,1,6) @E@@@Q      IF(A.EQ.1.OR.A.EQ.3.OR.A.EQ.5.OR.A.EQ.7.OR.A.EQ.DO
)@@G@@8.OR.A@B@@@Q     1.EQ.10.OR.A.EQ.0) BITS(START,7,6)=31@D@@@Q      IF(BITDP
)@@G@@S(START,7,6).NE.31) BITS(START,7,6)=30    @B@@@Q      IF(BITS(START,1,6)DQ
)@@G@@.NE.0) GO TO 11   @^@@@Q      BITS(START,1,6)=12@B@@@Q      BITS(START,1DR
)@@G@@3,6)=BITS(START,13,6)-1 @B@@@Q11    IF(BITS(START,1,6).NE.2) GO TO 10   DS
)@@G@@@^@@@Q      BITS(START,7,6)=28@^@@@Q      A=BITS(START,19,9)@B@@@Q      DT
)@@G@@IF(A/4*4.EQ.A) BITS(START,10,9)=29  @ @@@Q10    BITS(START,19,18)=0     DU
)@@G@@@B@@@Q      BITS(FINISH,1,18)=BITS(START,1,18)  @ @@@Q      BITS(FINISH,DV
)@@G@@19,18)=86400@^@@@Q      X1=BITS(START,1,9)@ @@@Q      X2=BITS(START,10,9DW
)@@G@@)     @ @@@Q      X3=BITS(START,19,9)     @C@@@Q      BITS(SDATE,1,18)=BDX
)@@G@@ITS(NUMBV(X1),1,18)     @C@@@Q      BITS(SDATE,19,18)=BITS(NUMBV(X2),1,1DY
)@@G@@8)    @C@@@Q      BITS(SDATE,37,18)=BITS(YEARV(X3),1,18)    @#@@@Q      DZ
)@@G@@STIME=0     @#@@@Q      VDATE=SDATE @#@@@Q      FTIME=86400 @B@@@Q      EA
)@@G@@IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,100) SDATE,VDATE  @B@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,300) SEB
)@@G@@TIME,FTIME  @#@@@Q12     CONTINUE   @C@@@Q      IF(PARAM.EQ.'HEADER')  REC
)@@G@@EAD(5,104) HEADR  @C@@@Q      IF(PARAM.EQ.'HEADER')  WRITE(6,204) HEADR ED
)@@G@@@B@@@Q      IF(PARAM.NE.'ALTER ')  GO TO 121    @^@@@Q      READ(5,99) AEE
)@@G@@LTERF @ @@@Q      WRITE(6,202) ALTERF     @^@@@Q      FILE(2)='      '  EF
)@@G@@@B@@@Q      BITS(FILE(3),1,36)=BITS(ALTERF,1,36)@B@@@Q      BITS(FILE(3)EG
)@@G@@,37,9)=BITS(ALTERF,37,9)@^@@@Q      FILREL(2)=FILE(2) @^@@@Q      FILRELEH
)@@G@@(3)=FILE(3) @ @@@Q      BITS(USEFIL(2),28,9)=' '@A@@@Q      BITS(USEFIL(EI
)@@G@@2),37,18)='  '    @^@@@Q      USEFIL(3)=FILE(3) @#@@@Q121   CONTINUE    EJ
)@@G@@@C@@@Q      IF(PARAM.EQ.'MAXCYC')  READ(5,105) NCYC   @C@@@Q      IF(PAREK
)@@G@@AM.EQ.'MAXCYC')  WRITE(6,205) NCYC  @ @@@Q      IF(NCYC.LE.30) GO TO 1  EL
)@@G@@@#@@@Q      WRITE(6,206)@#@@@Q      NCYC=30     @#@@@Q      GO TO 1     EM
)@@G@@@ @@@Q880   CALL CNVRTD(SDATE,DDATE)@^@@@Q88    FILREL(4)=FILE(4) @B@@@QEN
)@@G@@      IF(.NOT.FIRST) STATUS=FACSF2(FILREL)@ @@@Q      IF(NCYC.EQ.0) GO TEO
)@@G@@O 13  @ @@@Q      IF(BADINP) CALL EXIT    @ @@@Q      FILE(4)=FILENO(NCYEP
)@@G@@C)    @#@@@Q      NCYC=NCYC-1 @^@@@Q      USEFIL(4)=FILE(4) @^@@@Q      EQ
)@@G@@ERR=FACSF2(FILE)  @B@@@Q      IF(ERR.LT.0) WRITE(6,207) FILE,ERR  @ @@@QER
)@@G@@      IF(ERR.LT.0) GO TO 88   @^@@@Q      ERR=FACSF2(USEFIL)@C@@@Q      ES
)@@G@@IF(ERR.LT.0) WRITE(6,2071) USEFIL,ERR     @ @@@Q      IF(ERR.LT.0) CALL ET
)@@G@@EXIT  @^@@@Q      FIRST=.FALSE.     @ @@@Q      IF(ERR.LT.0) GO TO 88   EU
)@@G@@@A@@@QC     HERE WE START READING SYS$DEM$@#@@@Q      REWIND 11   @E@@@QEV
)@@G@@      READ(11,107,ERR=88) CYCDAT,CYCTIM      @ READ THE DATE@E@@@Q      EW
)@@G@@IF ((BITS(SDATE,1,18).EQ.BITS(CYCDAT,1,18)) .AND.     @D@@@Q     *(BITS(EX
)@@G@@SDATE,19,18).EQ.BITS(CYCDAT,19,18)) .AND. @F@@@Q     *(BITS(SDATE,37,18)EY
)@@G@@.EQ.BITS(CYCDAT,37,18))) SAMEDT = .TRUE.  @C@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,EZ
)@@G@@1071) CYCDAT,CYCTIM     @C@@@Q      IF(NOTFND.AND.SAMEDT) FRSTIM(1)=CYCTFA
)@@G@@IM(1) @C@@@Q      IF(NOTFND.AND.SAMEDT) FRSTIM(2)=CYCTIM(2) @B@@@Q      FB
)@@G@@IF(NOTFND.AND.SAMEDT) NOTFND=.FALSE.@ @@@Q      IF(NOTFND) GO TO 88     FC
)@@G@@@C@@@Q      IF(.NOT. SAMEDT.AND..NOT.SSET) GO TO 13   @D@@@Q      IF(SAMFD
)@@G@@EDT .AND.(SDATE.EQ.VDATE)) FINHER=.TRUE.  @F@@@Q      IF(.NOT. SAMEDT .AFE
)@@G@@ND.(SDATE.EQ.VDATE).AND.FINHER) GO TO 15  @C@@@QC     THIS FILE CONTAINSFF
)@@G@@ OUR START DATE DATA    @B@@@Q      IF(SDATE.NE.VDATE) SKPALT=.TRUE.    FG
)@@G@@@^@@@Q      NEXTIM=.FALSE.    @D@@@Q20    READ(11,106,ERR=88,END=88) PROFH
)@@G@@C,TIMIN,TIMOUT    @A@@@Q      IF(SKPALT) NEXTIM=.NOT.NEXTIM @^@@@Q      FI
)@@G@@TTIMIN=TIMIN/1000 @^@@@Q      TTMOUT=TIMOUT/1000@ @@@Q      NEWHR=TTIMINFJ
)@@G@@/3600+1     @B@@@Q      IF(TTIMIN.GT.STIME) SSET=.TRUE.     @E@@@Q      FK
)@@G@@IF(.NOT.SSET) GO TO 20          @ READ TILL TIME FOUND@C@@@QC     WE AREFL
)@@G@@ NOW PROPERLY POSITIONED IN THE FILE@C@@@Q      IF(FINHER.AND.FTIME.LE.TFM
)@@G@@TMOUT) GO TO 15   @ @@@Q      IF(.NOT.TIMSKP) GO TO 40@A@@@Q      IF(K.GFN
)@@G@@T.NUOMI) TIMSKP=.FALSE. @ @@@Q      IF(.NOT.TIMSKP) GO TO 40@F@@@Q      FO
)@@G@@IF(.NOT.(OMITS(K,1).EQ.CYCDAT.AND.OMITS(K,2).LT.TIMIN))     @#@@@Q     1FP
)@@G@@GO TO 30    @^@@@Q      SKIPIN=.NOT.SKIPIN@#@@@Q      K=K+1 .     @#@@@QFQ
)@@G@@30    CONTINUE    @ @@@Q      IF(SKIPIN) GO TO 20     @ @@@Q40    IF(.NOFR
)@@G@@T.EXCLUD) GO TO 60@^@@@Q      DO 41 L=1,III     @]@@@Q      LNG=6 @E@@@QFS
)@@G@@      IF(BITS(EXCLDD(L),46,9).EQ.BITS(AT5,46,9)) LNG=LNG-1  @E@@@Q      FT
)@@G@@IF(BITS(EXCLDD(L),37,18).EQ.BITS(AT4,37,18)) LNG=LNG-1@E@@@Q      IF((BIFU
)@@G@@TS(EXCLDD(L),28,9).EQ.BITS(AT3,28,9)) .AND.     @E@@@Q     *(BITS(EXCLDDFV
)@@G@@(L),37,18).EQ.BITS(AT3,37,18))) LNG=LNG-1 @ @@@Q      IF (LNG .LE. 4) THFW
)@@G@@EN    @#@@@Q      LNG=LNG*9   @E@@@Q      IF(BITS(PROC,1,LNG).EQ.BITS(EXFX
)@@G@@CLDD(L),1,LNG)) GO TO 20@]@@@Q      ELSE  @ @@@Q        LNG2 = (LNG - 4)FY
)@@G@@*9    @#@@@Q        LNG = 4*9 @F@@@Q        IF ((BITS(PROC,1,LNG).EQ.BITFZ
)@@G@@S(EXCLDD(L),1,LNG)) .AND.     @F@@@Q     *  (BITS(PROC,37,LNG2).EQ.BITS(GA
)@@G@@EXCLDD(L),37,LNG2))) GO TO 20 @]@@@Q      END IF@#@@@Q41    CONTINUE    GB
)@@G@@@D@@@Q60    IF(NEXTIM) GO TO 20  @ TAKE EVERY SECOND IMAGE  @ @@@Q      GC
)@@G@@TOTRES(INXTOT,1)=TIMIN  @A@@@Q      TOTRES(INXTOT,2)=TIMOUT-TIMIN @B@@@QGD
)@@G@@      BITS(PROCR,1,36) = BITS(PROC,1,36)  @B@R@Q      BITS(PROCR,37,18) GE
)@@G@@= BITS(PROC,37,18)@ @@@Q      TOTRES(INXTOT,3)=PROCR  @E@@@Q      IF(DEBGF
)@@G@@UG) WRITE(6,211)INXTOT,TOTRES(INXTOT,1),TOTRES  @A@@@Q     1(INXTOT,2),TGG
)@@G@@OTRES(INXTOT,3)   @^@@@Q      INXTOT=INXTOT+1   @ @@@Q      IF(.NOT.HOURGH
)@@G@@LY) GO TO 20@A@@@Q      IF(OLDHR.LT.NEWHR) GO TO 15   @#@@@Q      GO TO GI
)@@G@@20    @ @@@Q13    IF(NOTFND) WRITE(6,208) @C@@@Q      IF(DEBUG.AND.NOTFNGJ
)@@G@@D) WRITE(6,100) CYCDAT  @C@@@Q      IF(DEBUG.AND.NOTFND) WRITE(6,100) SDGK
)@@G@@ATE   @C@@@Q      IF(DEBUG.AND.NOTFND) WRITE(6,300) STIME   @C@@@Q      GL
)@@G@@IF(DEBUG.AND.NOTFND) WRITE(6,300) NCYC    @ @@@Q      IF(NOTFND) GO TO 9GM
)@@G@@99    @A@@@Q      IF(.NOT.SSET) WRITE(6,209)    @ @@@Q      IF(.NOT.SSETGN
)@@G@@) GO TO 999 @A@@@Q      IF(.NOT.FINHER) WRITE(6,210)  @A@@@Q      IF(.NOGO
)@@G@@T.FINHER) GO TO 999     @A@@@Q      IF(NCYC.EQ.0) HOURLY=.FALSE.  @^@@@QGP
)@@G@@15    INXTOT=INXTOT-1   @A@@@Q      IF(.NOT.HOURLY) GO TO 151     @A@@@QGQ
)@@G@@      IF(OLDHR.EQ.0) OLDHR=NEWHR    @A@@@Q      IF(OLDHR.EQ.NEWHR) GO TOGR
)@@G@@ 2002 @ @@@Q151   DO 363 INX=1,INXTOT     @^@@@Q      PASFLD(INX)=INX   GS
)@@G@@@#@@@Q363   CONTINUE    @^@T@S      INX = INX + 1     @^@@@T      INX = GT
)@@G@@INX - 1     @F@@@Q      CALL  REPORT(PASFLD,TOTRES,DDATE,SDATE,VDATE,HEAGU
)@@G@@DR,INREPT,  @G@U@Q     *DEBUG,SUMMAR,EXCLUD,INX,HOURLY,NUOMI,III,FRSTIM,GV
)@@G@@OMITS,EXCLDD)     @G@@@U     *DEBUG,SUMMAR,EXCLUD,INX,HOURLY,NUOMI,III,FGW
)@@G@@RSTIM,OMITS,EXCLDD,     @#@@@U     *PRNAME)     @^@@@Q      INREPT=.TRUEGX
)@@G@@.     @#@@@Q      INDX=INX    @A@@@Q      IF(.NOT.SUMMAR) GO TO 3666    GY
)@@G@@@^@@@Q      DO 3631 I=1,INXTOT@B@@@Q      IF(TOTRES(I,3).EQ.0) GO TO 363GZ
)@@G@@1     @^@@@Q      PRNAME=TOTRES(I,3)@E@@@Q      IF(BITS(PRNAME,1,9).NE.BHA
)@@G@@ITS(AT5P,46,9)) GO TO 3631    @]@@@Q      INX=0 @^@@@Q      DO 464 J=I,IHB
)@@G@@NXTOT @B@@@Q      IF(PRNAME.NE.TOTRES(J,3)) GO TO 464 @#@@@Q      INX=INHC
)@@G@@X+1   @^@@@Q      PASFLD(INX)=J     @E@@@Q      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,212)INHD
)@@G@@X,PASFLD(INX),TOTRES(J,3)     @^@@@Q      TOTRES(J,3)=0     @#@@@Q464   HE
)@@G@@CONTINUE    @ @@@QC     NOW CALL REPORT ROUTINES@F@@@Q      CALL  REPORTHF
)@@G@@(PASFLD,TOTRES,DDATE,SDATE,VDATE,HEADR,INREPT,  @G@U@Q     *DEBUG,SUMMARHG
)@@G@@,EXCLUD,INX,HOURLY,NUOMI,III,FRSTIM,OMITS,EXCLDD)     @G@@@U     *DEBUG,HH
)@@G@@SUMMAR,EXCLUD,INX,HOURLY,NUOMI,III,FRSTIM,OMITS,EXCLDD,     @#@@@U     *HI
)@@G@@PRNAME)     @#@@@Q3631  CONTINUE    @#@@@Q3666  CONTINUE    @ @@@QC     HJ
)@@G@@IF(CALCMP)  CALL CPLOT  @ @@@Q      IF(CALCMP)  WRITE(6,215)@A@@@Q      HK
)@@G@@IF(.NOT.DMPLOT) GO TO 3633    @^@@@Q      DO 3632 NN=1,97   @#@@@Q      HL
)@@G@@VECT(NN,1)=0@^@@@Q      VVECT(NN)=0.0     @#@@@Q3632  VECT(NN,2)=0@^@@@QHM
)@@G@@      DO 3634 NN=1,INDX @B@@@Q      MININX=TOTRES(NN,1)/(1000*60*15)    HN
)@@G@@@E@@@Q      VECT(MININX+1,1)=VECT(MININX+1,1)+(TOTRES(NN,2)/1000) @B@@@QHO
)@@G@@      VECT(MININX+1,2)=VECT(MININX+1,2)+1 @#@@@Q3634  CONTINUE    @^@@@QHP
)@@G@@      DO 3635 NN=1,97   @F@@@Q      IF(VECT(NN,2).GT.0) VVECT(NN)=FLOAT(HQ
)@@G@@VECT(NN,1))/FLOAT(VE    @#@@@Q     1CT(NN,2))   @#@@@Q3635  CONTINUE    HR
)@@G@@@E@@@Q      IF(.NOT.HOURLY)  CALL LNPLOT(VVECT,HEADR,PRNAME,DDATE,@#@@@QHS
)@@G@@     1INREPT)     @#@@@Q3633  CONTINUE    @A@@@Q      IF(.NOT.HOURLY) GOHT
)@@G@@ TO 999     @#@@@Q      INXTOT=1    @#@@@Q      OLDHR=NEWHR @E@@@Q2002  HU
)@@G@@IF(.NOT.((CYCDAT.NE.VDATE.AND.FINHER).OR.FINHER.AND.  @A@@@Q     1FTIME.HV
)@@G@@LE.TTMOUT)) GO TO 20    @#@@@Q999   CALL EXIT   @]@@@Q      END   _@@@@@HW
)@@G@@I).EQ.'LSTEXC') GO TO 3 @#@@@Q1111  CONTINUE    @^@@@Q3     IF (EXCLUD) HX
)@@G@@THEN  @#@@@Q        III=III-1 @#@@@Q        GO T*[S@@@*SDFF*@F@@@P      HY
)@@G@@SUBROUTINE REPORT(PASFLD,TOTRES,DDATE,SDATE,VDATE,HEADR,    @F@@@P     *HZ
)@@G@@INREPT,DEBUG,SUMMAR,EXCLUD,INX,HOURLY,NUOMI,III,FRSTIM,     @ @@@P     *IA
)@@G@@OMITS,EXCLDD,PRNAME)    @ @S@R      EXTERNAL FTIME(PL1)     @ @@@P      IB
)@@G@@IMPLICIT INTEGER(A-Z)   @ @T@S      EXTERNAL FTIME(PL1)     @A@@@P      IC
)@@G@@CHARACTER *8 STTIM, FINTIM    @A@@@P      REAL DDATE(3),SDATE*8,VDATE*8 ID
)@@G@@@C@@@P      DIMENSION TOTRES(10000,3), PASFLD(10000)  @B@@@P      DIMENSIE
)@@G@@ION  OMITS(60,2),FRSTIM(2)    @B@@@P      CHARACTER *6 EXCLDD(30), HEADRIF
)@@G@@(7)   @D@@@P      REAL LIMIT(11), CUMM(10), PCT(10),OCCUR(10)     @C@@@PIG
)@@G@@      REAL RQPM,RESPNS,TOTCUM,AVRGTM,ELAPST     @C@@@P      LOGICAL INREIH
)@@G@@PT,DEBUG,SUMMAR,HOURLY,EXCLUD @F@@@PC     COMMON /BLOCK/TOTRES,PASFLD,HEII
)@@G@@ADR,FRSTIM,CYCDAT,SUMMAR,     @E@@@PC    1HOURLY,INREPT,INX,DEBUG,PRNAMEIJ
)@@G@@,SDATE,OMITS,NUOMI,     @A@@@PC    2EXCLDD,EXCLUD,III,DDATE,VDATE @ @@@PIK
)@@G@@100   FORMAT(1H1,40X,7A6)     @E@@@P101   FORMAT(//' DATA COLLECTED ON  IL
)@@G@@',3A4,2X,'AT  ',2A4,    @#@@@P     1' HOURS')   @C@@@P1011  FORMAT(//40XIM
)@@G@@,' *** HOURLY ANALYSIS ***'//)@D@@@P102   FORMAT(/' MONITOR ELAPSED TIMEIN
)@@G@@ :',F8.1,' SEC ') @C@@@P1031  FORMAT(40X,'   ALL REQUESTS ANALYZED   ') IO
)@@G@@@C@@@P1032  FORMAT(/40X,' **************************')@C@@@P1033  FORMATIP
)@@G@@(40X,' **************************') @C@@@P104   FORMAT(/' NUMBER OF REQUIQ
)@@G@@ESTS   :',I6/)    @C@@@P105   FORMAT(' REQUESTS PER MINUTE  :',F6.1)    IR
)@@G@@@F@@@P106   FORMAT(//31X,' ----------  % OF REQUESTS WHICH WAITED FROM',IS
)@@G@@@^@@@P     1 '  ----------'/) @A@@@P107   FORMAT(7X,'PRO       NUM   '  IT
)@@G@@@E@@@P     1' AVG.    ZERO  .5    1.0   1.5   2.0   3.0   5.0'    @ @@@PIU
)@@G@@     2'   10.0  15.0  30.0')  @A@@@P108   FORMAT(7X,'CES        OF   '  IV
)@@G@@@E@@@P     1' WAIT    TO    TO    TO    TO    TO    TO    TO '    @ @@@PIW
)@@G@@     2'   TO    TO    +   ')  @A@@@P109   FORMAT(7X,'SOR       REQ   '  IX
)@@G@@@E@@@P     1' TIME    .5    1.0   1.5   2.0   3.0   5.0   10.0'   @ @@@PIY
)@@G@@     2'  15.0  30.0  SEC.'/)  @G@@@P110   FORMAT(7X,'-----    ----    --IZ
)@@G@@--    ----  ----  ----  ----  ----',@B@@@P     1 '  ----  ----  ----  --JA
)@@G@@--  ----')  @C@@@P111   FORMAT(7X,A6,1X,I6,3X,F5.2,2X,10F6.1)     @C@@@PJB
)@@G@@112   FORMAT(/15X,' CUMULATIVE %',1X,12F6.1)    @F@@@P115   FORMAT(1X,'IJC
)@@G@@NDX =',I3,2X,'TOTRES=',I6,2X,'DIVIDND=',F7.3)   @B@@@P120   FORMAT(1X,'FJD
)@@G@@RST =',I6,2X,'LAST=',I6)@E@@@P121   FORMAT(1X,'ELAPST =',F8.1,2X,'FRST='JE
)@@G@@,I9,2X,'LAST=',I9)@A@@@P122   FORMAT(1X,' OCCUR ',10F5.0)   @B@@@P123   JF
)@@G@@FORMAT(/' MONITORED PERIOD     : '/)@C@@@P124   FORMAT(15X,' START : ',AJG
)@@G@@6,2X,'AT',2X,A8)  @C@@@P125   FORMAT(15X,'  STOP : ',A6,2X,'AT',2X,A8)  JH
)@@G@@@E@@@P126   FORMAT(/' PROCESSORS EXCLUDED  :',2X,A6,2X,A6,2X,A6,  @D@@@PJI
)@@G@@     12X,A6,2X,A6,2X,A6,2X,A6,2X,A6,2X,A6,2X,A6/)     @B@@@P1271  FORMATJJ
)@@G@@(/' TIME PERIOD SKIPPED  :'/) @E@@@P127   FORMAT(24X,A6,1X,A6,A2,'    TOJK
)@@G@@    ',A6,1X,A6,A2/)     @#@@@P128   FORMAT(/)   @C@@@P      IF(INREPT.ANJL
)@@G@@D..NOT.HOURLY)  GO TO 2000    @^@@@P      WRITE(6,100) HEADR@D@@@P      JM
)@@G@@WRITE(6,101) DDATE(1),DDATE(2),DDATE(3),FRSTIM  @ @@@P      IF(HOURLY) WJN
)@@G@@RITE(6,1011)@^@@@P      WRITE(6,104) INX  @D@@@P      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,JO
)@@G@@120) PASFLD(1),PASFLD(INX)    @^@@@P      FRST=PASFLD(1)    @^@@@P      JP
)@@G@@LAST=PASFLD(INX)  @B@@@P      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,120) FRST,LAST    @F@@@PJQ
)@@G@@      IF(VDATE.EQ.SDATE) ELAPST=(TOTRES(LAST,1)-TOTRES(FRST,1)    @#@@@PJR
)@@G@@     1)/1000.     @A@@@P      FRST=TOTRES(FRST,1)/1000.     @A@@@P      JS
)@@G@@LAST=TOTRES(LAST,1)/1000.     @C@@@P      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,121) ELAPST,JT
)@@G@@FRST,LAST   @ @R@P      CALL TFMT(FRST,STTIM)   @ @@@R      CALL FTIME(FJU
)@@G@@RST,STTIM)  @ @R@P      CALL TFMT(LAST,FINTIM)  @ @@@R      CALL FTIME(LJV
)@@G@@AST,FINTIM) @#@@@P      WRITE(6,123)@ @@@P      WRITE(6,124)SDATE,STTIM JW
)@@G@@@ @@@P      WRITE(6,125)VDATE,FINTIM@E@@@P      IF(VDATE.EQ.SDATE.AND.NUJX
)@@G@@OMI.EQ.0) WRITE(6,102) ELAPST @^@@@P      WRITE(6,104) INX  @E@@@P      JY
)@@G@@IF(VDATE.EQ.SDATE.AND.NUOMI.EQ.0) RQPM=INX/ELAPST*60  @E@@@P      IF(VDAJZ
)@@G@@TE.EQ.SDATE.AND.NUOMI.EQ.0) WRITE(6,105) RQPM   @C@@@P      IF(EXCLUD) WKA
)@@G@@RITE(6,126)(EXCLDD(I),I=1,III)@A@@@P      IF(.NOT.NUOMI.GT.0) GO TO 1000KB
)@@G@@@^@@@P      WRITE(6,1271)     @^@@@P      DO 990 I=1,NUOMI,2@]@@@P      KC
)@@G@@J=I+1 @ @@@P      FRST=OMITS(I,2)/1000    @ @@@P      SECN=OMITS(J,2)/10KD
)@@G@@00    @ @R@P      CALL TFMT(FRST,STTIM)   @ @@@R      CALL FTIME(FRST,STKE
)@@G@@TIM)  @ @R@P      CALL TFMT(SECN,FINTIM)  @ @@@R      CALL FTIME(SECN,FIKF
)@@G@@NTIM) @D@@@P      WRITE(6,127) OMITS(I,1),STTIM,OMITS(J,1),FINTIM @#@@@PKG
)@@G@@990   CONTINUE    @^@@@P1000  WRITE(6,1032)     @^@@@P      WRITE(6,1031KH
)@@G@@)     @^@@@P      WRITE(6,1033)     @#@@@P2000  CONTINUE    @^@@@P      KI
)@@G@@DO 1001 I=1,10    @#@@@P      PCT(I)=0.0  @#@@@P      OCCUR(I)=0. @#@@@PKJ
)@@G@@1001  CUMM(I)=0.0 @#@@@P      LIMIT(1)=0. @#@@@P      LIMIT(2)=0.5@#@@@PKK
)@@G@@      LIMIT(3)=1.0@#@@@P      LIMIT(4)=1.5@#@@@P      LIMIT(5)=2.0@#@@@PKL
)@@G@@      LIMIT(6)=3.0@#@@@P      LIMIT(7)=5.0@^@@@P      LIMIT(8)=10.0     KM
)@@G@@@^@@@P      LIMIT(9)=15.0     @^@@@P      LIMIT(10)=30.0    @^@@@P      KN
)@@G@@LIMIT(11)=999.0   @^@@@P      DO 1111 I=1,INX   @^@@@P      INDEX=PASFLDKO
)@@G@@(I)   @G@@@P      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,115) INDEX,TOTRES(INDEX,2),TOTRES(INKP
)@@G@@DEX,2)/1.0E3@A@@@P      RESPNS=TOTRES(INDEX,2)/1.0E3  @^@@@P      DO 111KQ
)@@G@@1 J=1,10    @]@@@P      JJ=J+1@D@@@P      IF(RESPNS.GT.LIMIT(J).AND.RESPKR
)@@G@@NS.LE.LIMIT(JJ))  @ @@@P     1OCCUR(J)=OCCUR(J)+1.    @#@@@P1111  CONTINKS
)@@G@@UE    @A@@@P      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,122) OCCUR  @#@@@P      TOTCUM=0.0  KT
)@@G@@@^@@@P      DO 1112 J=1,10    @ @@@P      PCT(J)=OCCUR(J)/INX*100.@ @@@PKU
)@@G@@      CUMM(J)=TOTCUM+PCT(J)   @^@@@P      TOTCUM=CUMM(J)    @#@@@P1112  KV
)@@G@@CONTINUE    @C@@@P      IF(INREPT.AND..NOT.HOURLY)  GO TO 2001    @#@@@PKW
)@@G@@      WRITE(6,106)@#@@@P      WRITE(6,107)@#@@@P      WRITE(6,108)@#@@@PKX
)@@G@@      WRITE(6,109)@#@@@P      WRITE(6,110)@#@@@P2001  AVRGTM=0.0  @#@@@PKY
)@@G@@      DO 777 I=1,9@]@@@P      K=I+1 @B@@@P777   AVRGTM=LIMIT(K)*OCCUR(I)KZ
)@@G@@+AVRGTM     @B@@@P      AVRGTM=(AVRGTM+30.*OCCUR(10))/INX   @B@@@P      LA
)@@G@@IF(.NOT.INREPT) PRNAME='ALL   '     @D@@@P      WRITE(6,111)PRNAME,INX,ALB
)@@G@@VRGTM,(PCT(I),I=1,10)   @A@@@P      IF(.NOT.INREPT) WRITE(6,128)  @D@@@PLC
)@@G@@      IF(.NOT.SUMMAR) WRITE(6,112)(CUMM(I),I=1,10)    @]@@@P      RETURNLD
)@@G@@@]@@@P      END   @A@R@P      SUBROUTINE FTIME(SECNDS,TFMT) @E@R@PC     LE
)@@G@@THIS SUBROUTINE RECEIVES A TIME VALUE IN SECNDS AND   @E@R@PC     OF THELF
)@@G@@ FORM HHMMSS. A CHARACTER STRING OF THE FORM    @D@R@PC     HH:MM:SS IS LG
)@@G@@RETURNED THROUGH THE PARAMETER TFMT.@A@Q@P      IMPLICIT INTEGER (A-C,Q-LH
)@@G@@S)    @ @R@Q      IMPLICIT INTEGER (A-C)  @B@R@P      CHARACTER TFMT*8,SLI
)@@G@@ECS*6,BLANK*1     @#@R@P      BLANK = ' ' @D@R@P      IF (BITS(SECNDS,1,LJ
)@@G@@9) .EQ. BITS(BLANK,1,9)) THEN @C@R@P         BITS(SECS,1,27) = BITS(SECNLK
)@@G@@DS,10,27)   @C@R@P         BITS(SECS,28,9) = BITS(SECNDS,37,9)    @C@R@PLL
)@@G@@         BITS(SECS,37,9) = BITS(SECNDS,46,9)    @]@R@P      ELSE  @C@R@PLM
)@@G@@         BITS(SECS,1,36) = BITS(SECNDS,1,36)    @C@R@P         BITS(SECSLN
)@@G@@,37,18) = BITS(SECNDS,37,18)  @]@R@P      END IF@ @R@P      CHRL = TRMLELO
)@@G@@N(SECS)     @F@R@P      TFMT = SUBSTR(SECS,1,CHRL-4)//':'//SUBSTR(SECS,CLP
)@@G@@HRL-3,2)//  @A@R@P     *':'//SUBSTR(SECS,CHRL-1,2)    @]@R@P      RETURNLQ
)@@G@@@A@R@PC     END OF TIME FORMAT SUBROUTINE @]@R@P      END   _@@@@@CDIC),LR
)@@G@@EL ETKD1N 1GC*,D-DD(DE)*DLE C(@B@@@O^@)^@)^@1D9#*[S@@@*SDFF*@E@@@M      LS
)@@G@@SUBROUTINE LNPLOT (VECT,HEADR,PRNAME,DATE,SWITCH)     @F@Q@M      DIMENSLT
)@@G@@ION LINE(97),TIME(25),VECT(97),HEADR(7),BORDER(3)     @F@@@Q      DIMENSLU
)@@G@@ION LINE(97),TIME(25),VECT(97),HEADR(7),BORDER(3)     @^@O@M      DIMENSLV
)@@G@@ION DATE(2) @^@@@O      DIMENSION DATE(3) @^@@@M      LOGICAL SWITCH    LW
)@@G@@@D@N@M      CHARACTER TITLE(3)/' TOTAL',' RESPO','NSE   '/  @E@@@N      LX
)@@G@@CHARACTER *6 TITLE(3)/' TOTAL',' RESPO','NSE   '/     @#@N@M      INTEGELY
)@@G@@R TIME@ @P@N      INTEGER TIME,BORDR3     @A@@@P      INTEGER TIME,BORDRLZ
)@@G@@3,PRNAME    @A@N@M      CHARACTER BORDER,DATE,PRNAME  @B@O@N      CHARACMA
)@@G@@TER *6 BORDER,DATE,PRNAME     @A@P@O      CHARACTER *6 BORDER,PRNAME    MB
)@@G@@@A@Q@P      CHARACTER *6 BORDER,HEADR(7)  @A@@@Q      CHARACTER *6 BORDEMC
)@@G@@R,HEADR     @#@@@M      SCALE=2.0*10@^@@@M      WRITE (6,13) HEADR@^@@@MMD
)@@G@@      DO 9 I=50,1,-1    @#@@@M      J=I/10*10   @#@@@M      DO 3 N=1,3  ME
)@@G@@@^@@@M    3 BORDER(N)='      '@ @@@M      IF (I.NE.33) GO TO 5    @^@@@MMF
)@@G@@      BORDER(1)=TITLE(1)@B@Q@M      IF(.NOT.SWITCH) BORDER(1)=PRNAME    MG
)@@G@@@E@@@Q      IF(.NOT.SWITCH) BITS(BORDER(1),1,36)=BITS(PRNAME,1,36)@#@@@MMH
)@@G@@      DO 4 L=2,3  @^@@@M    4 BORDER(L)=TITLE(L)@#@@@M    5 CONTINUE    MI
)@@G@@@#@@@M      DO 6 K=2,97 @^@@@M    6 LINE(K)='      '  @#@@@M      LINE(1MJ
)@@G@@)='I' @ @@@M      IF (I.NE.J) GO TO 7     @#@@@M      LINE(1)='-' @^@@@MMK
)@@G@@      VALUE=SCALE*J/50  @#@@@M    7 CONTINUE    @#@@@M      DO 8 L=1,96 ML
)@@G@@@C@@@M      IF (VECT(L)*50/SCALE.GT.I-1) LINE(L+1)='*'@#@@@M    8 CONTINMM
)@@G@@UE    @B@@@M      IF (I.EQ.J) WRITE (6,14) VALUE,LINE @B@@@M      IF (I.MN
)@@G@@NE.J) WRITE (6,15) BORDER,LINE@#@@@M    9 CONTINUE    @#@@@M      DO 10 MO
)@@G@@I=1,97@#@@@M   10 LINE(I)='-' @^@@@M      DO 11 I=1,97,4    @#@@@M   11 MP
)@@G@@LINE(I)='I' @#@N@M      BORDER(3)=0 @#@@@N      BORDR3=0    @A@N@M      MQ
)@@G@@WRITE (6,14) BORDER(3),LINE   @ @@@N      WRITE (6,14) BORDR3,LINE@#@@@MMR
)@@G@@      DO 12 I=1,25@^@@@M   12 TIME(I)=(I-1)     @^@@@M      WRITE (6,16)MS
)@@G@@ TIME @A@O@M      WRITE(6,17) DATE(1),DATE(2)   @B@@@O      WRITE(6,17) MT
)@@G@@DATE(1),DATE(2),DATE(3) @]@@@M      RETURN@[@@@MC     @ @P@M13    FORMATMU
)@@G@@(1H1,51X,7A6)     @ @@@P13    FORMAT(1H1,51X,7A6)     @ @@@M   14 FORMATMV
)@@G@@ (1X,1PG18.3,97A1)@ @@@M   15 FORMAT (1X,3A6,97A1)    @^@@@M   16 FORMATMW
)@@G@@ (16X,25I4) @B@O@M   17 FORMAT (61X,'TIME (HOURS)',/61X,2A6)@B@P@O   17 MX
)@@G@@FORMAT (61X,'TIME (HOURS)',/61X,3A6)@B@@@P   17 FORMAT (61X,'TIME (HOURSMY
)@@G@@)',/61X,3A4)@]@@@M      END   _@@@@@@ @@@L^@)^@1AC)D-DD1  [D C.^9D^8)^@)MZ
)@@G@@@ @N@L^@)^@)^@)CLJEL^C(M @3 C.A@)^@)@^@@@N^@)^@)^@)CLJEL^EK3B*0^@)@D@N@LNA
)@@G@@^@)^@)^@)E9MDDOC*) @6 )1A)(^[]D9MC- EK*AS( -GDDI*[S@@@*SDFF*@A@@@@      NB
)@@G@@SUBROUTINE CNVRTD(SDATE,DDATE)@ @@@^      CHARACTER *9 DDDATE     @ @@@^NC
)@@G@@      CHARACTER *5 MONTH(12)  @#@@@^      REAL SDATE*8@A@@@^      DIMENSND
)@@G@@ION DDATE(3),MO(12)     @F@@@^      DATA MONTH/' JAN ',' FEB ',' MAR ','NE
)@@G@@ APR ',' MAY ',' JUN ', @D@@@^     *' JUL ',' AUG ',' SEP ',' OCT ',' NONF
)@@G@@V ',' DEC '/@F@@@^      DATA MO/'01','02','03','04','05','06','07','08',NG
)@@G@@'09','10',  @#@@@^     *'11','12'/  @#@@@^      DO 10 I=1,12@D@@@^      NH
)@@G@@IF (BITS(MO(I),1,18).EQ.BITS(SDATE,1,18)) THEN  @B@@@^      BITS(DDDATE,NI
)@@G@@1,18)=BITS(SDATE,37,18) @C@@@^      BITS(DDDATE,19,36)=BITS(MONTH(I),1,3NJ
)@@G@@6)    @C@@@^      BITS(DDDATE,55, 9)=BITS(MONTH(I),37,9)    @B@@@^      NK
)@@G@@BITS(DDDATE,64,18)=BITS(SDATE,19,18)@]@@@^      END IF@#@@@^10    CONTINNL
)@@G@@UE    @C@@@^      BITS(DDATE(1),1,36)=BITS(DDDATE,1,36)     @C@@@^      NM
)@@G@@BITS(DDATE(2),1,36)=BITS(DDDATE,37,36)    @B@@@^      BITS(DDATE(3),1,9)NN
)@@G@@=BITS(DDDATE,73,9)@A@^@@      DIMENSION DDATE(2),DDDATE(2)  @F@]@@      NO
)@@G@@FLD(0,6,INTER)=(10*(FLD(0,6,SDATE)-48))+(FLD(6,6,SDATE)-48) @C@^@]      NP
)@@G@@BITS(INTER,1,6)=(10*(BITS(SDATE,1,6)-48))+@ @#@]      *(BITS(SDATE,7,6)-NQ
)@@G@@48)   @ @^@#     *(BITS(SDATE,7,6)-48)    @G@]@@      FLD(6,6,INTER)=(10NR
)@@G@@*(FLD(12,6,SDATE)-48))+(FLD(18,6,SDATE)-48)     @D@^@]      BITS(INTER,7NS
)@@G@@,6)=(10*(BITS(SDATE,13,6)-48))+     @ @^@]     *(BITS(SDATE,19,6)-48)   NT
)@@G@@@G@]@@      FLD(12,6,INTER)=(10*(FLD(24,6,SDATE)-48))+(FLD(30,6,SDATE)-4NU
)@@G@@8)    @D@^@]      BITS(INTER,13,6)=(10*(BITS(SDATE,25,6)-48))+    @ @#@]NV
)@@G@@      *(BITS(SDATE,31,6)-48)  @ @^@#     *(BITS(SDATE,31,6)-48)   @ @^@@NW
)@@G@@      CALL DATED(INTER,DDDATE)@^@^@@      DDATE(1)=DDDATE(1)@^@^@@      NX
)@@G@@DDATE(2)=DDDATE(2)@]@@@@      RETURN@]@@@[      END   _@@@@@C)*AC2 )6 -NNY
)@@G@@*[S@@@*SDFF*@^@@@@          AXR$      .   @[@@@@$(1). @]@@@@DATED*    . NZ
)@@G@@@B@@@@          S         X11,SAVX11          . @B@@@@          E$DIT   OA
)@@G@@  EDDAT               . @D@@@@          LX        X11,SAVX11          .ROB
)@@G@@ESTORE X11  @G@@@@          L         A0,*0,X11           . GET INTER (TOC
)@@G@@DATE FORMAT DATE) @F@@@@          E$DAY2                        . CONVEROD
)@@G@@T TO DD MMM YY    @C@@@@          E$DITX                        . EXIT  OE
)@@G@@@B@@@@          L         X11,SAVX11          . @B@@@@          DL      OF
)@@G@@  A0,DATE             . @B@@@@          L         A2,1,X11            . OG
)@@G@@@D@@@@          DS        A0,0,A2             . INTO DDDATE @E@@@]      OH
)@@G@@    TZ        LTINT$              . CHECK FOR COMPILER@C@]@@          J OI
)@@G@@        2,X11               . RETURN@D@#@]          J         2,X11     OJ
)@@G@@          . E - RETURN  @D@@@#          J         2,X11               . OK
)@@G@@T - RETURN  @D@#@]          J         3,X11               . T - RETURN  OL
)@@G@@@D@@@#          J         3,X11               . E - RETURN  @B@@@@DATE  OM
)@@G@@    RES       5                   . @ @@@@EDDAT     E$PKT     2,DATE    ON
)@@G@@@B@@@@SAVX11    RES       1                   . @#@@@@          END     OO
)@@G@@___@@]          J       *[S@@@*SDFF*@ @[@@      IMPLICIT INTEGER (A-F)  OP
)@@G@@@A@@@[      SUBROUTINE FTIME(SECS,TMFMT)  @ @@@[      IMPLICIT INTEGER (OQ
)@@G@@S)    @ @[@@      EXTERNAL FTIME(PL1)     @D@[@@      CHARACTER D*8,T*8,OR
)@@G@@TFMT*8,FRST*6,D28*2,FLASH,SOE @ @[@@      CHARACTER *9 DDDATE     @A@[@@OS
)@@G@@      CHARACTER *8 CDATE/'00:00:00'/@^@]@[      CHARACTER *8 CDATE@^@@@]OT
)@@G@@      CHARACTER *8 TMFMT@^@@@[      TMFMT = '00:00:00'@A@[@@      CHARACOU
)@@G@@TER *2 CHOUR,CMINS,CSECS@ @[@@      CHARACTER *5 MONTH(12)  @ @[@@      OV
)@@G@@DIMENSION  TOTRES(2,2)  @^@[@@      REAL SDATE*8,REALR@A@[@@      DIMENSOW
)@@G@@ION DDATE(3),MO(12)     @F@[@@      DATA MONTH/' JAN ',' FEB ',' MAR ','OX
)@@G@@ APR ',' MAY ',' JUN ', @D@[@@     *' JUL ',' AUG ',' SEP ',' OCT ',' NOOY
)@@G@@V ',' DEC '/@F@[@@      DATA MO/'01','02','03','04','05','06','07','08',OZ
)@@G@@'09','10',  @#@[@@     *'11','12'/  @ @[@@75    FORMAT(1X,A,1X,A,1X,A)  PA
)@@G@@@B@[@@77    FORMAT(1X,I3,1X,I3,1X,I3,1X,I3)     @C@[@@80    FORMAT(1X,A,PB
)@@G@@A,1X,A,A,1X,A,A,1X,A,A,1X)    @ @[@@100   FORMAT(A8,1X,A8,1X,A8)  @ @[@@PC
)@@G@@101   FORMAT(1X,I6,1X,A8)     @ @[@@102   FORMAT(A8,1X,A6,1X,I4)  @^@[@@PD
)@@G@@103   FORMAT(A8,A8)     @ @[@@1031  FORMAT(1X,A6,5X,I9)     @^@[@@104   PE

)@@G@@FORMAT(1X,'DIVIDND=',F7.3,1X,'REALR=',F7.3)     @^@[@@107   FORMAT(A6,1XPG
)@@G@@,2A6) @^@[@@C     OUTPUT FORMATS    @#@[@@200   FORMAT(1H1) @D@[@@201   PH
)@@G@@FORMAT('*** UNKNOWN INPUT PARAMETER ',A6,'***') @^@[@@202   FORMAT(1H,A6PI
)@@G@@)     @^@[@@      CALL ADATE(D,T)   @^@[@@      WRITE(6,103) D,T  @^@[@@PJ
)@@G@@      LTIME = 13619     @#@[@@      DO 5 I=1,60 @^@]@@      LHOUR = LTIMPK
)@@G@@E/3600@^@@@]      LHOUR = SECS/3600 @B@]@@      LMINS = (LTIME - LHOUR*3PL
)@@G@@600)/60     @A@@@]      LMINS = (SECS - LHOUR*3600)/60@C@]@@      LSECS PM
)@@G@@= LTIME -(LHOUR*3600 + LMINS*60)    @C@@@]      LSECS = SECS -(LHOUR*360PN
)@@G@@0 + LMINS*60)     @^@[@@      NINE20 = 012789   @G@[@@      CHOUR=CHAR(BPO
)@@G@@ITS(LHOUR/10,31,6)) // CHAR(BITS(MOD(LHOUR,10),31,6)) @G@[@@      CMINS=PP

)@@G@@TS(MOD(LSECS,10),31,6)+48)    @]@@@[      RETURN@]@@@[      END   @D@[@@QC
)@@G@@C      CDATE=CHOUR // ':' // CMINS  // ':' // CSECS   @F@[@@C      BITS(QD

)@@G@@6,77) LHOUR,LMINS,LSECS @ @[@@      WRITE(6,100) D,CDATE,T  @^@[@@      QG
)@@G@@IF (I .EQ. 1) THEN@ @[@@         LTIME = LTIME + 1    @]@[@@      ELSE  QH
)@@G@@@ @[@@         LTIME = LTIME + 15   @]@[@@      END IF@#@[@@5     CONTINQI
)@@G@@UE    @C@[@@      WRITE(6,77) ICHAR(CHAR(BITS(NINE20,1,6))),@G@[@@     *QJ
)@@G@@ICHAR(CHAR(BITS(NINE20,7,6))),ICHAR(CHAR(BITS(NINE20,13,6))),     @A@[@@QK
)@@G@@     *ICHAR(CHAR(BITS(NINE20,19,6)))@D@[@@      WRITE(6,77) ICHAR(CHAR(BQL

)@@G@@     *CHAR(BITS(NINE20,13,6)) @F@[@@      WRITE(6,75) CHAR(BITS(NINE20,1QO
)@@G@@9,6)),CHAR(BITS(NINE20,25,6)),@ @[@@     *CHAR(BITS(NINE20,31,6)) @G@[@@QP
)@@G@@      WRITE(6,75) CHAR(MOD(LMINS,10)+48),CHAR(MOD(LSECS,10)+48),CHAR(50)QQ

)@@G@@(6,75) CHOUR,CMINS,CSECS@ @[@@      WRITE(6,100) D,CDATE,T  @#@[@@      QS
)@@G@@D28 = '28'  @#@[@@      S30 = '30'  @F@[@@      BITS(FLASH,1,9)=(10*(BITQT
)@@G@@S(D28,1,9)-48))+BITS(D28,10,9)-48   @F@[@@      BITS(SOE,1,9)=(10*(BITS(QU

)@@G@@E,FLASH,SOE,FLASH,SOE,FLASH   @A@[@@      BITS(SDATE,1,36)=BITS(D,1,36) QW
)@@G@@@B@[@@      BITS(SDATE,37,18)=BITS(D,37,18)     @ @[@@      WRITE(6,100)QX
)@@G@@ D,SDATE,T  @#@[@@      FRST = T    @ @[@@      CALL FFTIME(FRST,TFMT)  QY
)@@G@@@ @[@@      WRITE(6,100) T,FRST,TFMT@^@[@@      FFRST = 50523     @ @[@@QZ
)@@G@@      CALL CONVRT(FFRST,TFMT) @ @[@@      WRITE(6,101) FFRST,TFMT @ @[@@RA
)@@G@@      TOTRES(1,1) = 13605     @ @[@@      TOTRES(1,2) = 'MSG,'    @A@[@@RB
)@@G@@      WRITE(6,105) TOTRES(1,1)/1000.@A@[@@      REALR = TOTRES(1,1)/1.0ERC
)@@G@@3     @A@[@@      WRITE(6,106) TOTRES(1,1),REALR@ @[@@      INTER1=BITS(RD
)@@G@@SDATE,1,36) @ @[@@      INTER2=BITS(SDATE,37,18)@B@[@@      WRITE(6,102)RE
)@@G@@ SDATE,INTER1,INTER2    @B@[@@      WRITE(6,1031)  BITS(SDATE,37,9)     RF
)@@G@@@B@[@@      WRITE(6,1031)  10*(BITS(SDATE,37,9))@B@[@@      WRITE(6,1031RG
)@@G@@)  (BITS(SDATE,37,9)-48)@C@[@@      WRITE(6,1031)  (10*(BITS(SDATE,37,9)RH
)@@G@@-48)) @D@[@@      WRITE(6,1031)  BITS(SDATE,37,9)+BITS(SDATE,46,9)@G@[@@RI
)@@G@@      WRITE(6,1031)  (10*(BITS(SDATE,37,9)-48))+BITS(SDATE,46,9)-48     RJ
)@@G@@@A@[@@      WRITE(6,1031) BITS(SDATE,1,36)@ @[@@C     CALL DATED(SDATE,DRK
)@@G@@DDATE)@#@[@@      DO 10 I=1,12@D@[@@      IF (BITS(MO(I),1,18).EQ.BITS(SRL
)@@G@@DATE,1,18)) THEN  @A@[@@      WRITE(6,1031) BITS(MO(I),1,18)@A@[@@      RM
)@@G@@WRITE(6,1031) BITS(SDATE,1,18)@B@[@@      BITS(DDDATE,1,18)=BITS(SDATE,3RN
)@@G@@7,18) @C@[@@      BITS(DDDATE,19,36)=BITS(MONTH(I),1,36)    @C@[@@      RO
)@@G@@BITS(DDDATE,55, 9)=BITS(MONTH(I),37,9)    @B@[@@      BITS(DDDATE,64,18)RP
)@@G@@=BITS(SDATE,19,18)@]@[@@      END IF@#@[@@10    CONTINUE    @C@[@@      RQ
)@@G@@BITS(DDATE(1),1,36)=BITS(DDDATE,1,36)     @C@[@@      BITS(DDATE(2),1,36RR
)@@G@@)=BITS(DDDATE,37,36)    @B@[@@      BITS(DDATE(3),1,9)=BITS(DDDATE,73,9)RS
)@@G@@@D@[@@      WRITE(6,104) DDATE(1),DDATE(2),DDATE(3),DDDATE  @]@[@@      RT
)@@G@@STOP  @]@[@@      END   @A@[@@      SUBROUTINE FFTIME(SECNDS,TFMT)@A@[@@RU
)@@G@@      IMPLICIT INTEGER (A-C,Q-S)    @C@[@@      CHARACTER TFMT*8,SECNDS*RV
)@@G@@6, SECS*6,BLANK*1 @#@[@@      BLANK = ' ' @D@[@@      IF (BITS(SECNDS,1,RW
)@@G@@9) .EQ. BITS(BLANK,1,9)) THEN @C@[@@         BITS(SECS,1,27) = BITS(SECNRX
)@@G@@DS,10,27)   @C@[@@         BITS(SECS,28,9) = BITS(SECNDS,37,9)    @C@[@@RY
)@@G@@         BITS(SECS,37,9) = BITS(SECNDS,46,9)    @]@[@@      ELSE  @C@[@@RZ
)@@G@@         BITS(SECS,1,36) = BITS(SECNDS,1,36)    @C@[@@         BITS(SECSSA
)@@G@@,37,18) = BITS(SECNDS,37,18)  @]@[@@      END IF@ @[@@      CHRL = TRMLESB
)@@G@@N(SECS)     @F@[@@      TFMT = SUBSTR(SECS,1,CHRL-4)//':'//SUBSTR(SECS,CSC
)@@G@@HRL-3,2)//  @A@[@@     *':'//SUBSTR(SECS,CHRL-1,2)    @]@[@@      RETURNSD
)@@G@@@A@[@@C     END OF TIME FORMAT SUBROUTINE @]@[@@      END   _@@@@@AS1 C)SE
)@@G@@^[]DDOES*ET^CDOC*?AS7 )9 C)^@)@F@[@@^@)^@)^@)E9MDDOC**A0?AC0AS1 C)^@1A@%SF
)@@G@@ []DDOES*ET^CDOC*?AS7 )9 C(^@)@F@[@@^@)^@)^@)E9MDDOC**A0?AC0AS1 C)^@*CLDSG

)@@G@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@VF
)@@G@@SYSLIB$ID   75R1-H@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@VG
)@@G@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@VH
)@@G@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@*[S@@@*SDFF*@G@@@@C     ************************VI
)@@G@@******************************************@ @@@@C     PROGRAM :    PERTFVJ
)@@G@@OR    @B@]@@C     AUTHOR  :    Z.SORIC    3/10/77     @B@@@]C           VK
)@@G@@                  3/10/77     @G@@@@C     ******************************VL
)@@G@@************************************@D@@@@C     CONSTANTS    NODNUM = NUVM
)@@G@@MBER OF NODES ALLOWED   @G@@@@C                  NOD2/2 = MAX. POSSIBLE VN
)@@G@@NUMBER OF (POINTER,COST) PAIRS@D@@@@C     VECTORS :    PCOUNT = NUMBER OVO
)@@G@@F PREDECESSORS    @C@@@@C                  NCOST  = E.T.C FOR EACH NODE VP
)@@G@@@B@@@@C                  TABNOD = NODNAME VECTOR@D@@@@C                 VQ
)@@G@@ ICUR   = POINTERS INTO TOPOL ARRAY @C@@@@C     ARRAYS:      IPOINT = POVR
)@@G@@INTER,COST PAIRS  @D@@@@C                  SORTND = ORDERED SOURCE-DEST VS
)@@G@@NAMES @E@@@@C                  TOPOL  = TOPOLOGICALY ORDERED NODNAMES   VT
)@@G@@@G@@@@C     ************************************************************VU
)@@G@@******@^@@@@      PARAMETER NODNUM=7@A@@@@      PARAMETER NOD2=2*NODNUM-VV
)@@G@@2     @E@@@@      DIMENSION TABNOD(NODNUM), NCOST(NODNUM), ICUR(NOD2)   VW
)@@G@@@A@@@@      DIMENSION TOPOL(NOD2,NOD2)    @E@@@@      INTEGER PCOUNT(NODVX
)@@G@@NUM), IPOINT(NODNUM,NOD2), COST     @ @@@@      DIMENSION SORTND(NOD2,2)VY
)@@G@@@ @@@@100   FORMAT(A4,1X,A4,1X,I2)  @C@@@@110   FORMAT(//,T5,'NODNAME',TVZ
)@@G@@16,'E.T.C',//)    @ @@@@120   FORMAT(T5,A4,T16,I3)    @F@@@@200   FORMATWA
)@@G@@(1H1,T5,'INPUT DATA DESCRIBING PERT NETWORK',///T5,   @B@@@@     *'SOURCWB
)@@G@@E',T16,'DEST',T27,'COST',//)  @A@@@@300   FORMAT(T5,A4,T16,A4,T27,I2)   WC
)@@G@@@E@@@@400   FORMAT(////,T5,'NOD TABLE , POINTERS , COSTS ',//)    @ @@@@WD
)@@G@@500   FORMAT(T5,A4,3X,14I6)   @C@@@@770   FORMAT(//,T5,'TOPOLOGICAL NODEWE
)@@G@@ LIST ',//) @ @@@@880   FORMAT(T5,7(A4,3X))     @^@@@@C     PROGRAM STARWF
)@@G@@T     @ @@@@C     RESET VECTORS AND ARRAYS@^@@@@      DO 77 I=1,NODNUM  WG
)@@G@@@#@@@@      PCOUNT(I)=0 @#@@@@      NCOST(I)=0  @#@@@@      TABNOD(I)=0 WH
)@@G@@@#@@@@      ICUR(I)=0   @^@@@@      DO 77 J=1,NOD2    @^@@@@77    IPOINTWI
)@@G@@(I,J)=0     @G@@@@C     ************************************************WJ
)@@G@@******************@D@@@@C     THE FOLLOWING SECTION OF THE PROGRAM WILL WK
)@@G@@:     @A@@@@C     A.   READ AND PRINT INPUT DATA@D@@@@C     B.   ESTABLIWL
)@@G@@SH TABNOD AND IPOINT BY CALLING     @ @@@@C          UPDATE SUBROUTINE  WM
)@@G@@@A@@@@C     C.   PRINT TABNOD AND IPOINT  @G@@@@C     ******************WN
)@@G@@************************************************@]@@@@      LAST=0@#@@@@WO
)@@G@@      WRITE(6,200)@B@@@@1     READ(5,100,END=99) SOURCE,DEST,COST @A@@@@WP
)@@G@@      WRITE(6,300) SOURCE,DEST,COST @ @@@@      CALL UPDATE(SOURCE,I1)  WQ
)@@G@@@ @@@@      CALL UPDATE(DEST,I2)    @^@@@@      LAST2=2*LAST-2    @^@@@@WR
)@@G@@      DO 5 M=1,LAST2,2  @#@@@@      INT=M+1     @A@@@@      IF(IPOINT(I1WS
)@@G@@,M).EQ.0) GO TO 6 @#@@@@5     CONTINUE    @^@@@@6     IF(INT.GT.N) N=INTWT
)@@G@@@^@@@@      IPOINT(I1,M)=I2   @ @@@@      IPOINT(I1,M+1)=COST     @#@@@@WU
)@@G@@      GO TO 1     @#@@@@99    LAST2=N     @#@@@@      WRITE(6,400)@^@@@@WV
)@@G@@      DO 88 I=1,LAST    @D@@@@88    WRITE(6,500) TABNOD(I), (IPOINT(I,J)WW
)@@G@@, J=1,LAST2)@G@@@@C     ************************************************WX
)@@G@@******************@D@@@@C     THE FOLLOWING SECTION OF THE PROGRAM WILL WY
)@@G@@:     @ @@@@C     ESTABLISH PCOUNT VECTOR @G@@@@C     ******************WZ
)@@G@@************************************************@^@@@@      DO 299 I=1,LXA
)@@G@@AST   @^@@@@      DO 299 J=1,LAST2,2@^@@@@      K=IPOINT(I,J)     @B@@@@XB
)@@G@@      IF(K.GT.0) PCOUNT(K)=PCOUNT(K)+1    @#@@@@299    CONTINUE   @G@@@@XC
)@@G@@C     ******************************************************************XD
)@@G@@@D@@@@C     THE FOLLOWING SECTION OF THE PROGRAM WILL :     @A@@@@C     XE
)@@G@@A.  ESTABLISH NCOST VECTOR    @C@@@@C     B.  ESTABLISH SORTND ARRAY TO XF
)@@G@@BE USED FOR @ @@@@C         TOPOLOGICAL SORT    @B@@@@C     C.  PRINT NOXG
)@@G@@DE NAMES AND E.T.C'S    @G@@@@C     ************************************XH
)@@G@@******************************@]@@@@      LCNT=0@^@@@@333   DO 113 I=1,LXI
)@@G@@AST   @A@@@@      IF(PCOUNT(I).EQ.0) GOTO 199   @#@@@@113   CONTINUE    XJ
)@@G@@@#@@@@      GO TO 1000  @^@@@@199   DO 151 J=1,LAST2,2@^@@@@      K=IPOIXK
)@@G@@NT(I,J)     @B@@@@      IF(K.EQ.0.AND.J.GT.1) GO TO 333     @ @@@@      XL
)@@G@@IF(K.EQ.0) GO TO 152    @A@@@@      NETC1=IPOINT(I,J+1)+NCOST(I)  @B@@@@XM
)@@G@@      IF(NETC1.GT.NCOST(K)) NCOST(K)=NETC1@ @@@@      PCOUNT(K)=PCOUNT(KXN
)@@G@@)-1   @#@@@@      LCNT=LCNT+1 @ @@@@      SORTND(LCNT,1)=TABNOD(I)@ @@@@XO
)@@G@@      SORTND(LCNT,2)=TABNOD(K)@#@@@@152   PCOUNT(I)=-1@#@@@@151   CONTINXP
)@@G@@UE    @#@@@@      GO TO 333   @#@@@@1000  WRITE(6,110)@^@@@@      DO 16 XQ
)@@G@@I=1,LAST    @B@@@@16    WRITE(6,120) TABNOD(I), NCOST(I)    @G@@@@C     XR
)@@G@@******************************************************************@D@@@@XS
)@@G@@C     THE FOLLOWING SECTION OF THE PROGRAM WILL :     @B@@@@C     A.  ESXT
)@@G@@TABLISH TOPOL ARRAY BY CALLING@ @@@@C         SUBROUTINE TOPOLG   @B@@@@XU
)@@G@@C     B.  PRINT TOPOLOGICAL NODE LIST     @G@@@@C     ******************XV
)@@G@@************************************************@]@@@@      LAST=0@^@@@@XW
)@@G@@      DO 33 N=1,LCNT    @^@@@@      FROM=SORTND(N,1)  @^@@@@      TO=SORXX
)@@G@@TND(N,2)    @ @@@@      CALL TOPOLG(FROM,TO)    @#@@@@33    CONTINUE    XY
)@@G@@@#@@@@      WRITE(6,770)@^@@@@      DO 55 I=1,LAST    @^@@@@      INDEX=XZ
)@@G@@ICUR(I)     @B@@@@55    WRITE(6,880)(TOPOL(I,J),J=1,INDEX)  @]@@@@      YA
)@@G@@STOP  @G@@@@C     ******************************************************YB
)@@G@@************@A@@@@C     INTERNAL SUBROUTINE TOPOLG    @A@@@@C     CALL  YC
)@@G@@       TOPOLG(FROM,TO)  @ @@@@C     FROM= SOURCE NOD NAME   @ @@@@C     YD
)@@G@@TO  = DEST NOD NAME     @D@@@@C     SUBROUTINE WILL INSERT THE NEW PAIR YE
)@@G@@INTO TOPOL  @E@@@@C     ARRAY. VECTOR ICUR WILL POINT TO NUMBER OF ENTRIYF
)@@G@@ES    @E@@@@C     IN A PATH, VARIABLE LAST = NUMBER OF DIFFRENT PATHS.  YG
)@@G@@@G@@@@C     ************************************************************YH
)@@G@@******@A@@@@      SUBROUTINE TOPOLG(FROM,TO)    @#@@@@      IENTR=0     YI
)@@G@@@^@@@@      DO 71 I=1,LAST    @^@@@@      DO 71 J=2,LAST    @B@@@@      YJ
)@@G@@IF(FROM.EQ.TOPOL(I,J)) GO TO 15     @#@@@@      GO TO 71    @A@@@@15    YK
)@@G@@IF(ICUR(I).EQ.J) GO TO 55     @#@@@@      LAST=LAST+1 @#@@@@      DO 60 YL
)@@G@@K=1,J @ @@@@60    TOPOL(LAST,K)=TOPOL(I,K)@^@@@@      TOPOL(LAST,J+1)=TOYM
)@@G@@@^@@@@      ICUR(LAST)=J+1    @#@@@@      IENTR=1     @#@@@@      GO TO YN
)@@G@@71    @^@@@@55    TOPOL(I,J+1)=TO   @#@@@@      ICUR(I)=J+1 @#@@@@      YO
)@@G@@IENTR=1     @#@@@@71    CONTINUE    @ @@@@      IF(IENTR.GT.0) RETURN   YP
)@@G@@@#@@@@      LAST=LAST+1 @^@@@@      TOPOL(LAST,1)=FROM@^@@@@      TOPOL(YQ
)@@G@@LAST,2)=TO  @#@@@@      ICUR(LAST)=2@]@@@@      RETURN@G@@@@C     ******YR
)@@G@@************************************************************@A@@@@C     YS
)@@G@@INTERNAL SUBROUTINE UPDATE    @A@@@@C     CALL         UPDATE(SOURCE,K) YT
)@@G@@@C@@@@C     SOURCE= NOD NAME TO BE ENTERED INTO TABNOD@D@@@@C     K     YU
)@@G@@= RETURNED POINTER FOR SOURCE IN TABNOD   @D@@@@C     IF NOD NAME IS ALLYV
)@@G@@READY IN TABNOD, K WILL POINT @D@@@@C     TO ITS ENTRY. IF NOD NSME IS NYW
)@@G@@OT IN TABNOD,     @C@@@@C     NEW ENTRY AND NEW POINTER WILL BE CREATED YX
)@@G@@@G@@@@C     ************************************************************YY
)@@G@@******@A@@@@      SUBROUTINE UPDATE(ANOD,INDEX) @^@@@@      DO 11 K=1,LAYZ
)@@G@@ST    @#@@@@      INDEX=K     @A@@@@      IF(TABNOD(K).EQ.ANOD) RETURN  ZA
)@@G@@@#@@@@11    CONTINUE    @#@@@@      LAST=LAST+1 @#@@@@      INDEX=LAST  ZB
)@@G@@@^@@@@      TABNOD(INDEX)=ANOD@]@@@@      RETURN@]@@@@      END   _@@@@@ZC
)@@G@@DIMENSION  HEADR(7),FRSTIM(2) @B@@@5      DIMENSION EXCLDD(30), OMITS(60ZD
)@@G@@,2)   @D@@@5      REAL LIMIT(11), CUMM(10), PCT(*[S@@@*SDFF*@^@@@5      ZE
)@@G@@SUBROUTINE REPORT @ @@@5      IMPLICIT INTEGER(A-Z)   @A@@@5      DIMENSZF
)@@G@@ION STTIM(2), FINTIM(2) @^@@@5      DIMENSION DDATE(2)@C@@@5      DIMENSZG
)@@G@@ION TOTRES(10000,3), PASFLD(10000)  @A@@@5      DIMENSION  HEADR(7),FRSTZH
)@@G@@IM(2) @B@@@5      DIMENSION EXCLDD(30), OMITS(60,2)   @D@@@5      REAL LZI
)@@G@@IMIT(11), CUMM(10), PCT(10),OCCUR(10)     @C@@@5      REAL RQPM,RESPNS,TZJ
)@@G@@OTCUM,AVRGTM,ELAPST     @C@6@5      LOGICAL SELPRO,DEBUG,SUMMAR,HOURLY,EZK
)@@G@@XCLUD @C@@@6      LOGICAL INREPT,DEBUG,SUMMAR,HOURLY,EXCLUD @F@@@5      ZL
)@@G@@COMMON /BLOCK/TOTRES,PASFLD,HEADR,FRSTIM,CYCDAT,SUMMAR,     @E@6@5     1ZM
)@@G@@HOURLY,SELPRO,INX,DEBUG,PRNAME,SDATE,OMITS,NUOMI,     @E@@@6     1HOURLYZN
)@@G@@,INREPT,INX,DEBUG,PRNAME,SDATE,OMITS,NUOMI,     @A@@@5     2EXCLDD,EXCLUZO
)@@G@@D,III,DDATE,FDATE @ @@@5100   FORMAT(1H1,40X,7A6)     @F@@@5101   FORMATZP
)@@G@@(//' DATA COLLECTED ON  ',2A6,'AT  ',A6,A2,' HOURS')  @C@6@51011  FORMATZQ

)@@G@@J,1),FINTIM @#@@@5990   CONTINUE    @^@@@51000  WRITE(6,1032)     @A@6@5CA

)@@G@@@#@@@5      OCCUR(I)=0. @#@@@51001  CUMM(I)=0.0 @#@@@5      LIMIT(1)=0. CE

)@@G@@1.    @#@@@51111  CONTINUE    @A@@@5      IF(DEBUG) WRITE(6,122) OCCUR  CM

)@@G@@=OCCUR(J)/INX*100.@ @@@5      CUMM(J)=TOTCUM+PCT(J)   @^@@@5      TOTCUMCO
)@@G@@=CUMM(J)    @#@@@51112  CONTINUE    @ @9@6      IF(INREPT) GO TO 2001   CP
)@@G@@@C@@@9      IF(INREPT.AND..NOT.HOURLY)  GO TO 2001    @#@@@5      WRITE(CQ

)@@G@@    THIS IS THE II ACTIVITY. IT IS FORKED OFF   @D@@@V.         FROM MAIVB
)@@G@@N ACTIVITY TO ACCEPT COMMANDS TO    @^@@@V.         THE DRIVER.   @C@@@VVC
)@@G@@.         THE FOLOWING COMMANDS ARE RECOGNIZED: @E@@@V.            II DRVD
)@@G@@IVER TERMAL  -  TERMINATE ALL TERMINALS   @E@@@V.            II DRIVER TVE
)@@G@@ERMXX  -  TERMINATE XX TERMINALS    @E@@@V.            II DRIVER OPENXX VF
)@@G@@ -  OPEN XX NEW TERMINALS     @[@@@V.     @B@@@VIIACT*                  VG
)@@G@@                . @E@@@V          L,U       A0,'IIA'            . GET MEVH
)@@G@@ A NICE NAME@D@@@V          ER        NAME$               . AND NAME ME VI

)@@G@@ROUTINE IS USED TO PUT SITE PACKET  @A@@@V.         IN THE TIME WAIT QUEWU
)@@G@@UE.   @D@@@V.         IT WILL ACT THE TIMER IF THIS ONE IS ASLEEP @C@@@VWV
)@@G@@.         TO START MONITORING THE TWAIT QUEUE.  @B@@@V.         CALL    WW
)@@G@@ : L,U      A0,ACTPKT   @B@@@V.                    LMJ      X11,PUTTWQ  WX
)@@G@@@[@@@V.     @A@@@V.         NO REGISTERS DESTROYED    @]@@@VPUTTWQ*   . WY

)@@G@@    . INTO A1     @D@@@V          L         A0,SAVA0            . RESTORXD

)@@G@@    J         SHUFFL              . YUP, DO THE SHUFFLLE    @F@@@V      XZ
)@@G@@    L         A2,NEXT,A1          . NO, GRAB NEXT IN QUEUE  @F@@@V      YA
)@@G@@    JNZ       A2,$+3              . IS THIS THE LAST ONE?   @G@@@V      YB
)@@G@@    S         A0,NEXT,A1          . YES, INSERT AT THE BOTTOM     @C@@@VYC
)@@G@@          J         EXIT-1              . EXIT  @G@@@V          L       YD
)@@G@@  A3,A1               . SAVE PREVIOUS PACKET IN QUE   @E@@@V          L YE
)@@G@@        A1,A2               . POINT TO NEXT ONE @F@@@V          J       YF
)@@G@@  INNEW+1             . GO AND CHECK THIS ONE   @B@@@VSHUFFL            YG
)@@G@@                      . @F@@@V          TNE,H2    A3,QWORD            . YH
)@@G@@WAS THIS THE FIRST ONE? @G@@@V          J         REVRSE              . YI
)@@G@@YES, REVERSE FIRST AND NEW    @G@@@V          S         A0,NEXT,A3      YJ
)@@G@@    . NO, INSERT NEW IN BETWEEN     @D@@@V          S         A1,NEXT,A0YK
)@@G@@          . REPOINT     @D@@@V          J         EXIT                . YL
)@@G@@AND EXIT    @B@@@VREVRSE                                  . @F@@@V      YM
)@@G@@    S,H2      A0,QWORD            . MAKE NEW THE FIRST ONE  @E@@@V      YN
)@@G@@    S         A3,NEXT,A0          . REPOINT OLD ONE   @D@@@V          J YO
)@@G@@        EXIT                . AND EXIT    @[@@@V.     @^@@@VSAVA0     +0YP
)@@G@@        .   @^@@@VSAVA1     +0        .   @^@@@VSAVA2     +0        .   YQ
)@@G@@@^@@@VSAVA3     +0        .   @[@@@V/.    @D@@@V.         THIS IS TIMINGYR
)@@G@@ ACTIVITY. IT MONITORS THE    @D@@@V.         SITE PACKET TWAIT QUEUE ANYS
)@@G@@D QUEUES SITE     @D@@@V.         PACKETS THAT ARE READY FOR REACTIVATIOYT
)@@G@@N ON  @#@@@V.         ACTWQ.  @[@@@V.     @[@@@VTIMER*@F@@@V          L,YU
)@@G@@U       A0,'DIM'            . GET THIS TIMER A NAME   @D@@@V          ERYV
)@@G@@        NAME$               . AND NAME IT @F@@@V          S         A0,TYW
)@@G@@IMNAM           . SAVE FOR LATER ACTS     @E@@@VTIMAGN    TNZ,H2    QWORYX
)@@G@@D               . ANYBODY QUEUED?   @D@@@V          J         DEACT     YY
)@@G@@          . NO, DEACT   @E@@@V          TS        QCNTRL              . YZ
)@@G@@QUEUE ON QCNTRL   @E@@@V          ER        TIME$               . GRAB TZA
)@@G@@HE TIME     @E@@@V          L,H2      A3,QWORD            . GRAB THE QUEZB
)@@G@@UEEE  @E@@@V          JNZ       A3,DOTIM            . DO TIMING IF O.K. ZC
)@@G@@@D@@@VDEACTS    C$TS      QCNTRL              . CLEAR T/S   @F@@@VDEACT ZD
)@@G@@    TNZ       NUMOP               . ANY TERMINALS OPEN?     @G@@@V      ZE
)@@G@@    J         TERMIN              . NO, TERMINATE INPUT AND MYSELF@F@@@VZF
)@@G@@          SZ        TIMSLP              . TO SAY TIMER ASLEEP     @H@@@VZG
)@@G@@          ER        DACT$               . GO ASLEEP, PUTTWQ WILL AWAKE YZH
)@@G@@OU    @E@@@V          J         TIMAGN              . GO AND TIME AGAIN ZI
)@@G@@@B@@@VDOTIM                                   . @E@@@V          TLE     ZJ
)@@G@@  A0,TIMLFT,A3        . TIME EXPIRED?     @E@@@V          J         TWAIZK
)@@G@@T               . NO, WAIT SOME MORE@G@@@V          SZ        TIMLFT,A3 ZL
)@@G@@          . YES, CLEAR TIME LEFT CELL     @E@@@V          L         A1,NZM
)@@G@@EXT,A3          . GET NEXT IN QUE   @D@@@V          S,H2      A1,QWORD  ZN
)@@G@@          . UPDATE QWORD@F@@@V          L,H1      A1,QWORD            . ZO
)@@G@@NUMBER OF QUEUED PACKETS@D@@@V          AN,U      A1,1                . ZP
)@@G@@DECREMENT   @B@@@V          S,H1      A1,QWORD            . @H@@@V      ZQ
)@@G@@    LMJ       X11,PUTACQ          . QUE THE PACKET FOR REACTIVATION     ZR
)@@G@@@G@@@V          L,H2      A3,QWORD            . GRAB THE NEXT IN TWAIT QZS
)@@G@@UE    @F@@@V          JNZ       A3,DOTIM            . GO DOTIM IF NOT LAZT
)@@G@@ST    @F@@@V          J         DEACTS              . OTHERWISE CTS AND ZU
)@@G@@DEACT @D@@@VTWAIT     C$TS      QCNTRL              . CLEAR T/S   @E@@@VZV
)@@G@@          L,U       A1,30               . TAKE 30 MSECS     @D@@@V      ZW
)@@G@@    ER        TWAIT$              . AND WAIT    @F@@@V          J       ZX
)@@G@@  TIMAGN              . THEN GO AND TIME AGAIN  @G@@@VTERMIN            ZY
)@@G@@                      . HERE WE COME TO TERMINATE     @F@@@V          TZZZ
)@@G@@        DACTIN              . INPUT ACTIVITY DACTED?  @G@@@V          ERAA
)@@G@@        EXIT$               . NO, IT'LL TAKE CARE OF ITSELF @F@@@V      AB
)@@G@@    L         A0,INPNAM           . YES, HAVE TO WAKE HIM UP@B@@@V      AC
)@@G@@    ER        ACT$                . @D@@@V          ER        EXIT$     AD
)@@G@@          . AND EXIT    @[@@@V.     @D@@@V.         THIS SUBROUTINE IS UAE
)@@G@@SED BY THE TIMER TO PUT @D@@@V.         THE SITEID PACKET WITH EXPIRED TAF
)@@G@@IME WAIT ON @D@@@V.         THE ACTQW FOR REACTIVATION BY DISPATCHER.   AG
)@@G@@@[@@@V.     @B@@@VPUTACQ*                                 . @B@@@V      AH
)@@G@@    TS        ACTWRD              . @D@@@V          DS        A0,SAVA0  AI
)@@G@@          . SAVE A0,A1  @D@@@V          DS        A2,SAVA2            . AJ
)@@G@@SAVE A2,A3  @D@@@V          L,U       A1,ONACQ            . ON ACT QUEUEAK
)@@G@@@E@@@V          S         A1,FLAG,A3          . FLAG INTO PACKET  @E@@@VAL
)@@G@@          L,H2      A1,ACTQW            . GET THE POINTER   @G@@@V      AM
)@@G@@    JNZ       A1,INSRTN           . IF THERE, INSERT AT BOTTOM    @F@@@VAN
)@@G@@          S,H2      A3,ACTQW            . OTHERWISE QUEUE IT FIRST@F@@@VAO
)@@G@@EXIT1     SZ        NEXT,A3             . INDICATE THIS IS LAST   @F@@@VAP
)@@G@@          L,U       A1,1                . FOR REACTIVATION FLAG   @F@@@VAQ
)@@G@@          TZ        DACTIN              . INPUT ACTIVITY ASLEEP?  @F@@@VAR
)@@G@@          J         RSTOR               . NO, RESTORE AND RETURN  @E@@@VAS
)@@G@@          S         A1,DACTIN           . YES, AWAKE IT NOW @D@@@V      AT
)@@G@@    L         A0,INPNAM           . GET THE NAME@C@@@V          ER      AU
)@@G@@  ACT$                . ACT   @E@@@VRSTOR     DL        A0,SAVA0        AV
)@@G@@    . RESTORE A0,A1     @E@@@V          DL        A2,SAVA2            . AW
)@@G@@RESTORE A2,A3     @D@@@V          C$TS      ACTWRD              . CLEAR AX
)@@G@@T/S   @C@@@V          J         0,X11               . RETURN@B@@@VINSRTNAY
)@@G@@                                  . @F@@@V          L         A2,A1     AZ
)@@G@@          . SAVE PREVIOUS IN CHAIN  @E@@@V          L         A1,NEXT,A1BA
)@@G@@          . GRAB NEXT IN CHAIN@E@@@V          JNZ       A1,$-2          BB
)@@G@@    . LOOP UNTIL END    @E@@@V          S         A3,NEXT,A2          . BC
)@@G@@AND THEN INSERT   @C@@@V          J         EXIT1               . GO OUTBD
)@@G@@@[@@@V.     @B@@@VPROUT                                   . @B@@@V.     BE
)@@G@@    L         A0,(PF 1,4,OUTBUF) .  @B@@@V.         ER        APRINT$   BF
)@@G@@          . @B@@@V          J         0,X5                . @B@@@V      BG
)@@G@@    END       START               . ___0,('TERMAL')       . TO TERMINATEBH
)@@G@@ ALL? @C@@@V          J         TRMNTE              . YES   @F@@@V      BI
